%20%26quot%3BThe%20following%20decision%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20INDIA%20media%20committee%20in%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20held%20this%20afternoon.%20Judega%20Bharat%20Jeetega%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20condemned%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20to%20boycott%20certain%20shows%20of%20journalists%20and%20called%20their%20mindset%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20repressive%2C%20dictatorial%20and%20negative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20today%20strongly%20criticised%20and%20condemned%20the%20decision%20of%20all%20the%20constituents%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bghamandiya%26quot%3B%20alliance%20-%20I.N.D.I%20Alliance%20to%20boycott%20some%20journalists%20and%20the%20threat%20issued%20to%20them.%20By%20taking%20such%20a%20highly%20deplorable%20decision%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bghamandiya%26quot%3B%20alliance%20has%20once%20again%20revealed%20its%20highly%20repressive%2C%20dictatorial%20and%20negative%20mindset.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20severely%20criticises%20the%20unfortunate%20step%20of%20the%20I.N.D.I%20Alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBJP%20said%20that%20it%20severely%20opposes%20such%20a%20derogatory%20mentality%20which%20hinders%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20on%20Thursday%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20bloc-%20INDIA%20of%20%26quot%3Bbullying%20the%20media%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthreatening%20individual%20journalists%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20post%20on%20X%2C%20JP%20Nadda%20also%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Congress%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20several%20instances%20of%20'silencing'%20those%20with%20differing%20views.%20%26quot%3BThe%20history%20of%20Congress%20has%20many%20instances%20of%20bullying%20the%20media%20and%20silenc