%20and%2032%25%20of%20all%20exports%20from%20Peru.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20tanking%20economy%20will%20have%20a%20bigger%20impact%20on%20the%20US%20than%20some%20experts%20think%2C%20according%20to%20top%20economist%20David%20Rosenberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20op-ed%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinancialpost.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fwho-will-suffer-china-economic-downfall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Rosenberg%20Research%20founder%20and%20Atakan%20Bakiskan%2C%20a%20junior%20economist%20at%20Rosenberg's%20firm%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20potential%20spillover%20effects%20stemming%20from%20China's%20economy%2C%20which%20has%20floundered%20since%20dialing%20back%20its%20zero-COVID%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chinese%20economy%20has%20headed%20into%20a%20severe%20slowdown%2C%20with%20its%20economy%20entering%20deflationary%20terrain%20and%20the%20property%20sector%20remaining%20in%20crisis%20mode.%20The%20economic%20downfall%20will%20weigh%20negatively%20on%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20primarily%20through%20trade%20channels%20on%20countries%20with%20a%20high%20dependency%20on%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20and%20Bakiskan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commodities%20trade%20in%20particular%20will%20feel%C2%A0the%20effects%20of%20China's%20economic%20problems%2C%20and%20countries%20that%20are%20top%20exporters%20of%20key%20metals%20are%20exposed%2C%20Rosenberg%20and%20Bakiskan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20importers%20of%20copper%20and%20iron%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20nation%20purchases%2040%25%20of%20all%20exports%20from%20Chile%2C%2034%25%20of%20all%20exports%20from%20Australia%2C%20and%2032%25%20of%20all%20exports%20from%20Peru%2C%20putting%20those%20nations%20at%20highest%20risk%20of%20spillover%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20total%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20in%20China%20plunged%20to%20%245%20billion%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20from%20%24101%20billion%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202022%2C%20representing%20a%2095%25%20plunge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20when%20some%20pundits%20say%20'don't%20worry%20about%20the%20United%20States%2C%20it%20doesn't%20export%20much%20to%20China%2C'%20what%20is%20missing%20from%20that%20statement%20is%20that%20the%20US%20is%20in%20the%20top%20five%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20exposure%20in%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20economists%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20companies%20that%20operate%20there%20with%20a%20view%20towards%20serving%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20(and%20the%20rest%20of%20Asia)%20are%20surely%20going%20to%20see%20a%20dampening%20effect%20on%20their%20worldwide%20profits%20and%20from%20that%20indirect%20effect%2C%20end%20up%20having%20negative%20repercussions%20for%20the%20stock%20market%20(or%20at%20least%20those%20companies%20with%20footholds%20in%20China%20who%20will%20be%20affected).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20warned%20that%20Beijing%20could%20even%20risk%20an%20economic%20crisis%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20grapple%20with%20a%20litany%20of%20problems%2C%20including%20high%20debt%20loads%2C%20poor%20demand%2C%20a%20failing%20property%20sector%2C%20and%20deflation.%20But%20the%20economic%20outlook%20could%20perk%20up%20so%20long%20as%20China%20keeps%20monetary%20policy%20appropriately%20loose%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-debt-deflation-housing-market-demographics-japan-morgan-stanley-2023-8%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-us-spillover-debt-deflation-property-crisis-david-rosenberg-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694719207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5731084352bcd01b008c1efb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-us-spillover-debt-deflation-property-crisis-david-rosenberg-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Total%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20in%20China%20plunged%20to%20%245%20billion%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20from%20%24101%20billion%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-us-spillover-debt-deflation-property-crisis-david-rosenberg-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20MLA%20Arrested%20Over%20Violence%20In%20Haryana's%20Nuh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Congress%20MLA%20from%20Haryana%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20July%2031%20communal%20violence%20in%20Haryana's%20Nuh.%20Mamman%20Khan%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Ferozepur%20Jhirka%2C%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20one%20of%20the%20First%20Information%20Reports%20registered%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Nuh%20Police%20last%20week.%20He%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20on%20Friday.%3Cbr%3EOf%20the%2052%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%2042%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20one%20is%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20Mamman%20Khan%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20and%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bample%20evidence%26quot%3B%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20has%20told%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20that%20the%20police%20have%20the%20phone%20call%20records%20and%20other%20evidence%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20Additional%20Advocate%20General%20Deepak%20Sabharwal%20told%20the%20court%20that%20Mamman%20Khan%20was%20named%20an%20accused%20on%20September%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA%20had%20appealed%20to%20the%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20seeking%20protection%20from%20arrest%20and%20claiming%20he%20was%20being%20framed%20in%20the%20case.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20not%20in%20Nuh%20the%20day%20the%20violence%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA's%20counsel%20said%20he%20has%20come%20to%20know%20only%20now%20that%20he%20has%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustice%20Vikas%20Bahl%20will%20hear%20the%20case%20on%20October%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViolence%20broke%20out%20in%20Nuh%20during%20a%20procession%20by%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20on%20July%2031.%20Six%20people%20were%20killed.%20A%20cleric%20died%20in%20an%20attack%20on%20a%20mosque%20in%20adjoining%20Gurugram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20MLA%20pleaded%20that%20all%20cases%20related%20to%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh%20should%20be%20transferred%20to%20a%20special%20investigation%20team.%20The%20team%20has%20been%20formed%20already%2C%20the%20government%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20MLA%20was%20asked%20twice%20by%20Nuh%20Police%20to%20join%20the%20investigation%20but%20he%20failed%20to%20appear%20before%20it.%20He%20did%20not%20come%20for%20questioning%20on%20August%2031%2C%20saying%20he%20had%20viral%20fever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20said%20he%20was%20at%20his%20Gurugram%20home%20from%20July%2026%20to%20August%201%2C%20and%20not%20in%20Nuh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20government's%20counsel%20said%20the%20evidence%20was%20against%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20reported%20PTI.%20Mr%20Sabharwal%20said%20there%20were%20call%20detail%20records%2C%20his%20location%20tracked%20through%20a%20phone%20tower%2C%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20MLA's%20personal%20security%20officer%20and%20other%20evidence%20that%20indicated%20that%20the%20claim%20was%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20counsel%20told%20the%20court%20that%20a%20co-accused%2C%20Taufiq%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20September%209%20has%20also%20named%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20said%20calls%20were%20exchanged%20between%20them%20on%20July%2029%20and%2030%2C%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694718060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frh2ui1k_nuh-_625x300_11_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mla-arrested-over-violence-in-haryanas-nuh-4391169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Congress%20MLA%20from%20Haryana%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20July%2031%20communal%20violence%20in%20Haryana's%20Nuh.%20Mamman%20Khan%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Ferozepur%20Jhirka%2C%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20one%20of%20the%20First%20Information%20Reports%20registered%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mla-arrested-over-violence-in-haryanas-nuh-4391169%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mla-arrested-over-violence-in-haryanas-nuh-4391169%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mla-arrested-over-violence-in-haryanas-nuh-4391169%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Higher%20for%20longer%20interest%20rates%20won't%20derail%20the%20bull%20market%20rally%20in%20stocks%2C%20chief%20stock%20strategist%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bull%20and%20bear%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65034b80992da60019ec9cc6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFollowing%20a%20glut%20of%20IPOs%20in%202021%2C%20broader%20market%20and%20economic%20uncertainty%20has%20led%20to%20a%202022%20tech%20IPO%20hiatus.%3Cp%3EiStock%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigher%20for%20longer%20interest%20rates%20won't%20derail%20the%20bull%20market%20in%20stocks%2C%20according%20to%20BMO's%20Brian%20Belski.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBelski%20highlighted%20that%20stocks%20have%20performed%20just%20fine%20during%20elevated%20interest%20rate%20periods%20based%20on%20market%20history.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BS%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20had%20better%20risk%20adjusted%20returns%20during%20periods%20of%20higher%20interest%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EA%20period%20of%20higher%20for%20longer%20interest%20rates%20isn't%20enough%20to%20derail%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-new-bull-rally-economy-employment-upside-ahead-2023-6%5C%22%3Ethe%20current%20bull%20market%20in%20stocks%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20a%20Wednesday%20note%20from%20BMO's%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20Brian%20Belski.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelski%20observed%20that%20based%20on%20historical%20analysis%20of%20data%20going%20back%20to%201979%2C%20the%20stock%20market%20performs%20just%20fine%20during%20periods%20of%20elevated%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20interest%20rates%20are%20%26quot%3Bunderstandably%20uncomfortable%20for%20some%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20since%202009%2C%20interest%20rates%20have%20been%20at%20historically%20low%20levels%2C%20until%20last%20year%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-hike-july-inflation-powell-recession-federal-reserve-2023-7%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%20started%20to%20aggressively%20hike%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20bid%20to%20tame%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20entire%20generation%20of%20investors%20grew%20up%20during%20an%20extreme%20period%20of%20near-zero%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20high%20interest%20rates%20aren't%20all%20that%20bad%20for%20the%20stock%20market%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20found%20that%20returns%20tend%20to%20be%20slightly%20below%20average%20and%20interestingly%20a%20bit%20less%20volatile%20compared%20to%20lower%20interest%20rate%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20had%20better%20risk%20adjusted%20returns%20during%20periods%20of%20higher%20interest%20rates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelski%20found%20that%20on%20a%20one-year%20rolling%20basis%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20gained%20an%20average%208.2%25%20during%20high%20interest%20rate%20periods%2C%20compared%20to%2010.6%25%20during%20low%20interest%20rate%20periods.%20But%20with%20those%20higher%20returns%20came%20significantly%20higher%20risk%2C%20with%20a%20standard%20deviation%20of%2018%25%20compared%20to%20just%2012.7%25%20during%20periods%20of%20high%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStandard%20deviation%20helps%20investors%20measure%20the%20amount%20of%20risk%20they%20are%20taking%20on%20relative%20to%20the%20average%20gains%20they%20can%20expect%20when%20buying%20a%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20what%20works%20well%20during%20periods%20of%20higher%20interest%20rates%2C%20Belski%20highlighted%20cyclical%20sectors%20like%20technology%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20industrials.%20Meanwhile%2C%20more%20defensive%20sectors%20underperformed%20the%20market%2C%20like%20utilities%20and%20health%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20makes%20sense%20to%20us%20since%20rising%20interest%20rates%20are%20usually%20an%20indication%20of%20stronger%20economic%20growth%20as%20the%20bond%20market%20readjusts%20levels%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broader%20US%20economy%20is%20indeed%20still%20growing%20and%20on%20a%20solid%20foundation%20with%20unemployment%20near%20historically%20low%20levels.%20The%20Atlanta%20Fed's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww