20Fled%2C%20They%20Will%20Complete%20Money%20Trail%3A%20CID%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20critics%20and%20supporters%20of%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20are%20debating%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20his%20arrest%20and%20its%20political%20impact%2C%20NDTV's%20Uma%20Sudhir%20spoke%20exclusively%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20CID%20chief%20N%20Sanjay%20to%20ask%20how%20they%20concluded%20that%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20the%20end%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20alleged%20AP%20Skill%20Development%20Scam%2C%20and%20what%20they%20are%20doing%20about%20a%20key%20file%20that%20has%20gone%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20agency%20chief%20denied%20he%20is%20acting%20on%20the%20diktat%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20but%20suggested%20that%20a%20former%20finance%20secretary%20who%20had%20contradicted%20the%20CID's%20claims%20must%20have%20done%20so%20under%20pressure.%20The%20CID%20chief%20listed%20out%20other%20cases%20that%20they%20are%20investigating%20against%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20his%20son%20Nara%20Lokesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20unusual%20move%2C%20Mr%20Sanjay%20and%20additional%20advocate%20general%20P%20Sudhakar%20came%20to%20Hyderabad%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20media%20and%20explain%20the%20details%20of%20Mr%20Naidu's%20involvement%20in%20the%20alleged%20AP%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%20scam%20and%20why%20he%20needed%20to%20be%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20how%20the%20scam%20was%20linked%20to%20Mr%20Naidu%20becoming%20the%20end-beneficiary%2C%20the%20CID%20chief%20told%20NDTV%20a%20key%20aide%20of%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20P%20Srinivas%2C%20who%20had%20worked%20as%20his%20personal%20assistant%20for%20years%2C%20had%20gone%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSrinivas%20was%20examined%20by%20the%20IT%20department%20and%20as%20you%20know%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20was%20recently%20served%20IT%20notices%20for%20suspected%20unaccounted%20income%20of%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore.%20This%20person%20has%20run%20away.%20He%20was%20linked%20with%20another%20two%20persons%20involved%20in%20generating%20fake%20invoices%20who%20were%20questioned%20by%20ED%20and%20IT.%20This%20shows%20that%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20of%20Rs%20241%20crore%20clearly%20points%20the%20finger%20at%20the%20end-beneficiary.%20That%20is%20a%20gap%20in%20our%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CID%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20income%20tax%20had%20reportedly%20raided%20Mr%20Srinivas%20house%20and%20found%20receipts%20and%20transactions%20tracing%20to%20his%20superior%2C%20that%20is%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20Mr%20Sanjay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20denied%20aspersions%20being%20cast%20on%20him%20that%20he%20was%20working%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20chief%20minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investigations%20began%20in%202018%20when%20GST%20noticed%20irregularities.%20When%20accused%20people%20and%20shell%20company%20people%20tried%20to%20avail%20of%20GST%20benefits%20out%20of%20their%20greed%20and%20out%20of%20their%20jostling%20among%20each%20other%20to%20benefit%20from%20GST.%20we%20booked%20FIR%20in%202021.%20the%20way%20the%20money%20was%20pushed%20out%20of%20the%20system%20was%20arbitrary%20and%20it%20calls%20for%20high-level%20pressure%20and%20involvement%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%20High%20level%20officers%20have%20made%20notings.%20We%20are%20working%20along%20with%20the%20ED%20and%20IT%20on%20this%2C%20%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20questioned%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20that%20arrested%20several%20people%2C%20had%20not%20named%20Mr%20Naidu%20as%20a%20suspect%20or%20questioned%20him%2C%20Mr%20Sanjay%20said%3A%20%60%60We%20are%20linking%20this%20to%20Mr%20Naidu%20because%20of%20the%20way%20corporation%20came%20into%20existence%20with%20an%20ulterior%20motive.%20Appointing%20outsiders%20to%20head%20govt%20agency%2C%20giving%20four%20posts%20to%20one%20man%20and%20timely%20siphoning%20of%20money%20even%20before%20execution%20and%20before%20any%20third%20party%20compliance%20or%20assessment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20the%20CID%20has%20issued%20a%20look-out%20notice%20for%20Mr%20Srinivas%2C%20who%20the%20CID%20says%20would%20be%20a%20key%20evidence%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Mr%20Sanjay%20said%20they%20were%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Srinivas%20was%20served%20notice%20to%20appear%20before%20us.%20But%20he%20ran%20away%20to%20the%20US.%20Another%20key%20witness%20Manoj%20also%20ran%20away%20to%20Middle%20East%2C%20shows%20the%20pressure%20given%20the%20high-profile%20person%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20denying%20he%20was%20working%20under%20any%20political%20pressure%2C%20Mr%20Sanjay%20said%20PV%20Ramesh%2C%20former%20finance%20secretary%2C%20who%20had%20questioned%20the%20action%20of%20the%20CID%20in%20arresting%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20could%20be%20acting%20under%20some%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%2C%20whose%20statement%20to%20the%20CID%20was%20quoted%20as%20a%20reason%20to%20arrest%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20had%20told%20NDTV%20that%20his%20statement%20was%20misunderstood%20or%20twisted%20by%20the%20CID.%20%26quot%3BThe%20officers%20should%20be%20questioned%20to%20fix%20responsibility.%20How%20can%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20had%20said%20a%20key%20file%20in%20the%20APSSDC%20had%20gone%20missing%20and%20all%20the%20claims%20were%20being%20made%20based%20on%20semi-official%20records%20in%20a%20shadow%20file%20maintained%20in%20the%20finance%20department.%20So%20when%20was%20the%20file%20noted%20to%20be%20missing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20CID%20scanner%20in%20the%20last%2018%20months%2C%20whatever%20we%20tried%20to%20trace%20the%20file.%20It%20could%20have%20gone%20missing%20in%20the%20earlier%20era%20itself%20sinc