Dhariwal%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20urban%20development%20and%20housing%20minister%20made%20the%20remarks%20during%20the%20press%20conference%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhariwal%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bparental%20pressure%26quot%3B%20is%20another%20reason%20behind%20suicide%20by%20students%20in%20Kota%2C%20a%20coaching%20hub.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20NEET%20aspirant%20Richa%2C%20who%20reached%20Kota%20from%20Ranchi%20on%20Thursday%20morning%20to%20receive%20her%20body%2C%20expressed%20strong%20objection%20to%20Mr%20Dhariwal's%20remarks%20and%20demanded%20evidence%20to%20prove%20his%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20daughter%20did%20not%20have%20any%20affair.%20If%20he%20(Dhariwal)%20has%20any%20such%20evidence%2C%20he%20should%20share%20it%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ravindra%20Sinha%2C%20the%20girl's%20father%2C%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20his%20daughter%20had%20complained%20to%20him%20that%20some%20boys%20in%20Kota%20would%20tease%20her%20while%20going%20to%20and%20coming%20from%20a%20coaching%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Sinha%20also%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20over%20counselling%20facilities%20to%20coaching%20students%20in%20Kota.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20Dhariwal%20could%20not%20be%20contacted%20for%20comment%20on%20Sinha's%20demand%20for%20an%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Circle%20Inspector%20of%20Vigyan%20Nagar%20police%20station%20Davesh%20Bhardwaj%2C%20who%20is%20also%20investigation%20officer%20in%20the%20latest%20suicide%20case%2C%20denied%20having%20recovered%20any%20suicide%20note%20from%20Richa's%20hostel%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20refuted%20love%20affair%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20suicide%20by%20the%20girl%20saying%20police%20did%20not%20find%20any%20such%20clue%20from%20her%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20lodged%20a%20case%20under%20Section%20174%20of%20CrPC%2C%20Bhardwaj%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20girl's%20body%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDSP%20Dharmveer%20Singh%20also%20denied%20of%20recovering%20any%20note%20suggesting%20love%20affair%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20girl's%20suicide.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%20The%20family%20members%20decided%20to%20perform%20the%20girl's%20last%20rites%20at%20an%20electric%20crematorium%20in%20Kota%20itself%2C%20the%20DSP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20was%20a%20class%2011%20student%20and%20was%20preparing%20for%20NEET%20in%20a%20coaching%20institute%20here%20since%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20figures%2C%20Richa%20became%20the%2023rd%20student%20who%20committed%20suicide%20in%20Kota%20this%20year%2C%20the%20highest%20ever%20for%20the%20country's%20coaching%20hub.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20figure%20was%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694713260000%2C%2