.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-opens-up-about-her-equation-with-shah-rukh-khan-i-am-one-of-the-few-people-he-is-vulnerable-with%2Farticleshow%2F103671811.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Bloc%20Criticises%20Modi's%20'Celebrations'%20on%20Day%203%20Officers%20Were%20Killed%20in%20Kashmir%20Militant%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14225747%2Fimage-1315.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Opposition%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20lashed%20out%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20participating%20in%20celebrations%20at%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20office%2C%20hailing%20his%20successful%20leadership%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20on%20a%20day%20when%20three%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsouth-kashmir-officers-killed-attack%5C%22%3Ewere%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20militant%20attack%20in%20south%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20(September%2013)%2C%20the%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%2C%20Colonel%20Manpreet%20Singh%2C%20based%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kokernag%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsouth-kashmir-officers-killed-attack%5C%22%3Ekilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20with%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20(DSP)%2C%20Humayun%20Muzamil%20Bhat%2C%20and%20Major%20Aashish%20Dhonchak%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20Modi%20received%20a%20grand%20welcome%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%20where%20party%20workers%20gathered%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20congratulate%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20conducting%20the%20G20%20summit.%20Modi%20was%20showered%20with%20flower%20petals%2C%20as%20he%20took%20a%20victory%20lap%20around%20the%20BJP%20office%20and%20met%20party%20workers%20who%20offered%20him%20flowers%20and%20congratulated%20him%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%20(September%2014)%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Congress%20Ex-Servicemen%20Department%2C%20Colonel%20Rohit%20Chaudhary%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20is%20very%20disheartening%20and%20painful%20to%20note%20that%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20ji%20has%20shown%20utter%20disrespect%20and%20insensitivity%20towards%20the%20sacrifices%20made%20by%20our%20brave%20soldiers.%20While%20our%20soldiers%20(were)%20fighting%20the%20battle%20with%20Pakistan-sponsored%20terrorists%20in%20Anantnag%2C%20and%20news%20had%20come%20out%20about%20the%20death%20of%20our%20three%20soldiers%20and%20some%20were%20wounded%2C%20but%20Modi%20ji%20was%20doing%20his%20own%20Mahima%20Mandan%20in%20his%20own%20BJP%20headquarters%20by%20his%20own%20BJP%20people%20%E2%80%93%20who%20were%20showering%20flowers%20on%20him%20and%20Modi%20ji%20was%20projecting%20his%20grandeur%20image%20in%20front%20of%20the%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20families%20of%20the%20soldiers%20are%20grieving%2C%20the%20entire%20nation%20was%20shocked%20with%20the%20sad%20news.%20The%20Indian%20Army%20was%20continuing%20its%20cordon%20and%20search%20operations%20in%20the%20hot%20bed%20area%20of%20the%20militancy%20but%20the%20BJP%20cadres%20continued%20their%20celebration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20also%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20celebration%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20and%20asked%20why%20Modi%20could%20not%20postpone%20the%20celebration%20by%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20utterly%20shocking%20is%20that%20PM%20Modi%20chose%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccelebrate%20himself%20for%20G20%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20BJP%20HQ%20yesterday%20with%20a%20grand%20party%20AFTER%20these%20bravehearts%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20%26amp%3B%20the%20news%20was%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EModi%20shamelessly%20celebrates%20while%20our%20bravehearts%20lay%20down%20their%20lives%20%F0%9F%91%87%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYesterday%20our%20bravehearts%20DySP%20Humayan%20Bhat%2C%20Maj%20Ashish%20Dhonack%2C%20%26amp%3B%20Col%20Manpreet%20Singh%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20while%20combating%20terrorists%20in%20Anantnag%2C%20J%26amp%3BK.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20nation%20is%20eternally%20indebted%20to%20them%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Saket%20Gokhale%20(%40SaketGokhale)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSaketGokhale%2Fstatus%2F1702162149886550122%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCouldn%E2%80%99t%20Modi%20postpone%20his%20self%20PR%20for%20just%201%20day%3F%20Did%20BJP%20have%20to%20celebrate%20%26amp%3B%20glorify%20Modi%20when%20such%20a%20tragedy%20has%20occurred%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20demanded%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20why%20the%20celebrations%20could%20not%20be%20postponed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20BJP%20should%20tell%20the%20country%20what%20was%20such%20an%20important%20%E2%80%98celebration%E2%80%99%20that%20could%20not%20be%20postponed%20for%20two%20days%20in%20honour%20of%20the%20supreme%20dedication%20of%20the%20officers%20and%20soldiers%20of%20our%20armed%20forces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20she%20%E2%80%9Cexpected%20more%20se