t%20%26quot%3BSanatan%20Dharma.%26quot%3B%20The%20BJP%20has%20linked%20these%20remarks%20to%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20putting%20them%20in%20a%20difficult%20position.%20The%20PM%20invoked%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20other%20historical%20figures%20to%20criticize%20the%20opposition%20and%20urged%20followers%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20to%20be%20vigilant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-congress-sanatan-dharma-bjp-madhya-pradesh-elections-india-opposition-alliance-dmk-udyanidhi-stalin-a-raja%2Farticleshow%2F103670039.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWilling%20To%20Retire%20If...%26quot%3B%3A%20Himanta%20Sarma%20On%20Allegations%20Against%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma's%20wife%20Riniki%20Bhuyan%20Sarma%20today%20said%20she%20would%20files%20a%20Rs%2010%20crore%20defamation%20case%20against%20Congress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20over%20his%20allegation%20that%20her%20company%20has%20taken%20a%20Rs%2010%20crore%20central%20subsidy.%3Cbr%3E%C2%A0%3Cbr%3EThere%20has%20been%20an%20intense%20war%20of%20words%20between%20Mr%20Gogoi%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20since%20yesterday%20over%20Mrs%20Sarma's%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20receiving%20a%20credit-linked%20subsidy%20from%20the%20Central%20Government.%3Cbr%3E%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BPride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20is%20an%20independent%20entity%20in%20existence%20since%202006%20with%20business%20interests%20in%20varied%20sectors.%20It%20is%20a%20law-abiding%20company%20with%20all%20its%20financial%20records%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20With%20a%20long%20and%20successful%20business%20track%20record%2C%20Pride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd.-%20like%20any%20other%20qualifying%20enterprise%20-%20is%20eligible%20to%20participate%20in%20government-supported%20programs%2Fincentive%20schemes.%20However%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20pertaining%20to%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20Sampada%20Scheme%2C%20Pride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd%20has%20neither%20claimed%20or%20received%20a%20single%20paisa%20of%20government%20subsidy%2C%20despite%20meeting%20all%20the%20eligible%20criteria%2C%26quot%3B%20Riniki%20Bhuyan%20Sarma%20tweeted%20in%20X.%3Cbr%3E%C2%A0%3Cbr%3EAttaching%20Lok%20Sabha%20replies%2C%20Mr%20Gogoi%20had%20initially%20posted%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20day%20yesterday%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20parroted%20one%20line%20regarding%20his%20wife's%20firm.%20For%20his%20benefit%20I%20am%20stating%20the%20reply%20of%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Piyush%20Goyal%20in%20Parliament.%20Piyush%20Goyal's%20reply%20has%20exposed%20the%20truth%20and%20both%20Ministers%20need%20to%20clarify%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOut%20of%20respect%20I%20will%20offer%20my%20free%20advice%20to%20the%20company%20linked%20to%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20which%20has%20received%20approval%20for%20a%20Rs%2010%20crore%20grant%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20Please%20make%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Pallab%20Das%20a%20party%20to%20the%20case.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6O3oJ7wKz2%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6O3oJ7wKz2%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20(%40GauravGogoiAsm)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGauravGogoiAsm%2Fstatus%2F1702290065651900488%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reply%20itself%20clarifies%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20released%20any%20funds%20to%20the%20mentioned%20company.%20I%20want%20to%20emphasize%20once%20again%20that%20neither%20my%20w