an%20too%20cut%20his%20teeth%20in%20tape%20ball%20cricket%20in%20Mirpur%2C%20a%20small%20village%20in%20PoK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20daily%20wage%20workers%2C%20Zaman%20was%20drawn%20to%20cricket%20from%20a%20very%20young%20age%20and%20found%20backing%20from%20his%20household%20to%20pursue%20his%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20and%20brothers%20are%20labourers.%20I%20started%20playing%20cricket%20after%20watching%20other%20boys%20in%20my%20street%20playing%20that%20sport.%20I%20used%20to%20skip%20classes%20at%20Madrasa%20to%20play%20cricket.%20One%20of%20my%20relatives%20told%20me%20to%20take%20part%20in%20an%20under-16%20trial%20in%20my%20village%20after%20seeing%20how%20fast%20I%20was%20bowling.%20Fortunately%2C%20I%20got%20selected%20and%20my%20journey%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20Zaman%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20by%20PCB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZaman%20took%20the%20next%20step%20when%20he%20was%20picked%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20under-19%20team%20to%20tour%20Australia%2C%20an%20experience%20he%20termed%20as%20an%20eye-opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pacer's%20first%20big%20stage%20experience%20came%20when%20he%20was%20picked%20by%20Lahore%20Qalandars%20for%20Pakistan%20Super%20League%20(PSL)%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20cathartic%20for%20him%20to%20rub%20shoulders%20with%20top%20stars%20of%20his%20country%20such%20as%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Haris%20Rauf%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112775-haris-rauf-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHaris%20Rauf%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZaman%20made%20a%20mighty%20impression%20in%20his%20first%20PSL%20season%2C%20taking%2018%20wickets%20from%2013%20matches%20to%20finish%20third%20on%20the%20wicket-takers'%20chart%20behind%20Afridi%20(20)%20and%20leg-spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shadab%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107566-shadab-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShadab%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20(19).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20effort%20had%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20Lahore%20winning%20their%20maiden%20PSL%20title%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20saw%20him%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20T20%20league%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20draft%20him%20into%20the%20side.%20He%20was%20quick%20and%20had%20wonderful%20yorker%2C%20and%20we%20thought%20that%20he%20could%20be%20a%20good%20fit%20into%20our%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Waqas%20Ahmed%2C%20the%20bowling%20coach%20of%20Qalandars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20observation%20was%20not%20far%20from%20truth%20as%20Zaman%20made%20his%20presence%20felt%20in%20PSL%202023%20as%20well%2C%20grabbing%2015%20wickets%20from%2013%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helped%20the%20Qalandars%20to%20retain%20their%20title%2C%20the%20first%20team%20in%20the%20PSL%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20bit%20raw%20when%20he%20came%20to%20us.%20He%20has%20that%20roundarm%20action.%20He%20was%20quick%20alright%20but%20he%20tended%20to%20stray%20the%20ball%20down%20the%20leg%20side%20or%20way%20outside%20the%20off-stump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20worked%20on%20the%20accuracy%20factor%20at%20nets%20and%20he%20is%20a%20hardworking%20boy%20and%20a%20quick%20learner%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20he%20has%20this%20ability%20to%20bowl%20fast%20full-length%20deliveries%2C%20we%20always%20wanted%20to%20use%20him%20at%20the%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmed%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZaman's%20skill%20was%20visible%20when%20he%20defended%2012%20runs%20in%20the%20last%20over%20of%20the%20PSL%202023%20final%20against%20Multan%20Sultans%20on%20March%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20days%20later%20Zaman%20made%20his%20Pakistan%20debut%20in%20a%20T20I%20against%20Afghanistan%20at%20Sharjah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pakistan%20needed%20a%20replacement%20for%20Naseem%2C%20team%20director%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mickey%20Arthur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F42542-j