plane%E2%80%99s%20direction%20changed%20due%20to%20the%20swing%20and%20it%20turned%20180%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20official%20further%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20flights%20had%20to%20be%20diverted%20to%20other%20cities%2C%20as%20one%20runway%20is%20used%20each%20day%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694702532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2FMumbai_Airport_domestic_aerial.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fpilots-of-a-private-jet-critically-injured-after-plane-skids-off-mumbai-airport-runway%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20runway%20at%20Mumbai%20airport%20was%20closed%2C%20and%20all%20flights%20were%20diverted%20to%20Goa%20and%20Ahmedabad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fpilots-of-a-private-jet-critically-injured-after-plane-skids-off-mumbai-airport-runway%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NASA%20Panel%20Calls%20For%20Agency%20To%20Play%20Larger%20Role%20In%20Studying%20UFOs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20NASA%20panel%20recommended%20in%20a%20report%20issued%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20increase%20its%20efforts%20to%20gather%20information%20on%20unidentified%20objects%20in%20the%20sky%20-%20labeled%20%26quot%3Bunidentified%20anomalous%20phenomenon%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20UAP%2C%20by%20the%20government%20-%20and%20play%20a%20larger%20role%20in%20helping%20the%20Pentagon%20detect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20accompanying%20the%20report%2C%20said%20it%20was%20evaluating%20the%20independent%20study%20team's%20findings%20and%20recommendations%20but%20nonetheless%20created%20a%20new%20role%2C%20director%20of%20UAP%20research.%20The%20NASA%20panel%2C%20comprising%20experts%20in%20scientific%20fields%20ranging%20from%20physics%20to%20astrobiology%2C%20issued%20the%20report%20after%20holding%20its%20first%20public%20meeting%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUAP%20are%20better%20known%20to%20the%20public%20as%20unidentified%20flying%20objects%2C%20or%20UFOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNASA%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20existing%20and%20planned%20Earth-%20and%20space-observing%20assets%2C%20together%20with%20an%20extensive%20archive%20of%20historic%20and%20current%20data%20sets%2C%20which%20should%20be%20directly%20leveraged%20to%20understand%20UAP%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20NASA's%20fleet%20of%20Earth-observing%20satellites%20typically%20lack%20the%20spatial%20resolution%20to%20detect%20relatively%20small%20objects%20such%20as%20UAP%2C%20their%20state-of-the-art%20sensors%20can%20be%20directly%20utilized%20to%20probe%20the%20state%20of%20the%20local%20earth%2C%20oceanic%2C%20and%20atmospheric%20conditions%20that%20are%20spatially%20and%20temporally%20coincident%20with%20UAPs%20initially%20detected%20via%20other%20methods.%20Thus%2C%20NASA's%20assets%20can%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20by%20directly%20determining%20whether%20specific%20environmental%20factors%20are%20associated%20with%20certain%20reported%20UAP%20behaviors%20or%20occurrences%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20has%20made%20several%20disclosures%20of%20information%20it%20has%20gathered%20regarding%20a%20subject%20that%20once%20was%20met%20by%20virtual%20official%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20report%20called%20UAPs%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20our%20planet's%20greatest%20mysteries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObservations%20of%20objects%20in%20our%20skies%20that%20cannot%20be%20identified%20as%20balloons%2C%20aircraft%20or%20natural%20known%20phenomena%20have%20been%20spotted%20worldwide%2C%20yet%20there%20are%20limited%20high-quality%20observations.%20The%20nature%20of%20science%20is%20to%20explore%20the%20unknown%2C%20and%20data%20is%20the%20language%20scientists%20use%20to%20discover%20our%20universe's%20secrets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20numerous%20accounts%20and%20visuals%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20consistent%2C%20detailed%2C%20and%20curated%20observations%20means%20we%20do%20not%20presently%20have%20the%20body%20of%20data%20needed%20to%20make%20definitive%2C%20scientific%20conclusions%20about%20UAP%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20issued%20a%20watershed%20report%20in%202021%20compiled%20by%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%20in%20conjunction%20with%20a%20Navy-led%20task%20force%20encompassing%20numerous%20observations%20-%20mostly%20from%20military%20personnel%20of%20UAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20included%20some%20UAP%20cases%20that%20previously%20came%20to%20light%20in%20the%20Pentagon's%20release%20of%20video%20from%20naval%20aviators%20showing%20enigmatic%20aircraft%20off%20the%20US%20East%20and%20West%20Coasts%20exhibiting%20speed%20and%20maneuverability%20exceeding%20known%20aviation%20technologies%20and%20lacking%20any%20visible%20means%20of%20propulsion%20or%20flight-control%20surfaces.%20The%20report%20said%20defense%20and%20intelligence%20analysts%20lacked%20sufficient%20data%20to%20determine%20the%20nature%20of%20some%20of%20the%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20independent%20NASA%20panel%20studying%20UAPs%20held%20its%20first%20public%20meeting%20in%20June%2C%20comprising%20experts%20in%20scientific%20fields%20ranging%20from%20physics%20to%20astrobiology.%20Challenges%20panel%20members%20cited%20to%20their%20work%20included%20a%20stigma%20attached%20to%20the%20subject%20as%20well%20as%20a%20dearth%20of%20scientifically%20reliable%20methods%20for%20documenting%20UFOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20senior%20US%20defense%20intelligence%20officials%20told%20a%202022%20congressional%20hearing%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20was%20committed%20to%20determining%20the%20origins%20of%20UAPs.%20Both%20officials%20pledged%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20would%20follow%20the%20evidence%20wherever%20it%20leads%20and%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20primary%20interest%20is%20addressing%20possible%20national%20security%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20officials%20in%20that%20hearing%20chose%20their%20words%20carefully%20including%20the%20question%20of%20possible%20extraterrestrial%20origins.%20One%20of%20the%20officials%2C%20Scott%20Bray%2C%20said%20during%20the%20hearing%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20no%20material%2C%20we%20have%20detected%20no%20emanations%2C%20within%20the%20UAP%20task%20force%20that%20would%20suggest%20it%20is%20anything%20non-terrestrial%20in%20origin.%26quot%3B%20There%20had%20been%20no%20open%20congressional%20hearing%20on%20the%20subject%20since%20the%20Air%20Force%20terminated%20an%20inconclusive%20UFO%20program%20code-named%20Project%20Blue%20Book%20in%201969.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20congressional%20hearing%20was%20held%20in%20July%20that%20included%20testimony%20from%20retired%20military%20personnel%2C%20though%20no%20government%20officials%20appeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694702400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fism5nirg_nasa-generic-original-please-dont-use-with-afp-credit-_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-panel-calls-for-agency-to-play-larger-role-in-studying-ufos-4390312%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20NASA%20panel%20recommended%20in%20a%20report%20issued%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20increase%20its%20efforts%20to%20gather%20information%20on%20unidentified%20objects%20in%20the%20sky%20-%20labeled%20%26quot%3Bunidentified%20anomalous%20phenomenon%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20UAP%2C%20by%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%