2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F22122938%2FSwiggy-delivery-waiting_PTI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F22122938%2FSwiggy-delivery-waiting_PTI.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F22122938%2FSwiggy-delivery-waiting_PTI-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F22122938%2FSwiggy-delivery-waiting_PTI-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-499746%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recognition%20of%20the%20gig%20worker%20in%20the%20legal%20framework%20acts%20as%20a%20hindrance%20in%20furthering%20their%20demands.%20This%20recognition%20is%20derived%20from%20classifications%20drawn%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20cases%20when%20the%20term%20gig%20work%20didn%E2%80%99t%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERulings%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20point%20to%20certain%20classification%20tests%20that%20help%20determine%20the%20status%20of%20the%20worker.%20Such%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fgig-workers-should-be-included-under-the-industrial-disputes-act%2F%5C%22%3Erulings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20have%20relied%20on%20rigid%20definitions%20of%20an%20employee%2C%20where%20the%20status%20of%20the%20gig%20worker%20is%20not%20recognised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20determination%20of%20an%20employee%20in%20contrast%20to%20an%20independent%20contract%20in%20the%20view%20of%20the%20law%2C%20depends%20on%20the%20tests%20of%20classification%20used%2C%20with%20the%20control%20test%20being%20the%20most%20used%20on%20this%20issue.%20However%2C%20if%20one%20were%20to%20apply%20a%20more%20progressive%20test%2C%20one%20would%20see%20that%20these%20workers%20do%20fall%20under%20the%20definition%20of%20an%20employee-employer%20relationship%2C%E2%80%9D%20comments%20Sabreen%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20OP%20Jindal%20University%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrouble%20at%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20participation%20of%20women%20in%20this%20workforce%20(with%20numbers%20ranging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Feducation-today%2Fjobs-and-careers%2Fstory%2Fdespite-rise-in-gig-economy-women-s-participation-still-less-than-30-1985236-2022-08-08%5C%22%3Ebelow%2030%25%3C%2Fa%3E)%C2%A0%20is%20also%20limited%20due%20to%20the%20vague%20categorisation%20of%20the%20worker.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F164.52.210.154%3A8080%2Fjspui%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F1751%2F1%2F1623414147_pub_Engendering_gig_economy_in_India_-_Policy_Brief.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Indian%20Social%20Sciences%20Trust%20on%20%3Cem%3EWomen%20Workers%20in%20the%20Gig%20Economy%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehighlights%20women%20workers%20receive%20lower%20pay%20and%20less%20favourable%20contracts%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIssues%20of%20harassment%20also%20tend%20to%20get%20swept%20under%20the%20rug%2C%20with%20women%20choosing%20to%20stay%20at%20home%20rather%20than%20be%20out%20on%20the%20roads%20late%20at%20night.%20Despite%20the%20welcoming%20policy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.swiggy.com%2F2022%2F11%2F21%2Fswiggy-introduces-sexual-harassment-policy-for-female-delivery-executives%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520the%2520event%2520of%2520a%2Ca%2520complaint%2520with%2520the%2520company.%5C%22%3Eadopted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Swiggy%20last%20year%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20harassment%20at%20the%20workplace%20in%20companies%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpudr.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2021-12%2FPUDR%2520report%2520on%2520gig%2520workers-%2520Behind%2520the%2520Veil%2520of%2520Algorithms.pdf%5C%22%3EUrban%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Uber%20have%20discouraged%20women%20from%20participating%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosts%20associated%20with%20the%20work%20also%20often%20get%20borne%20by%20the%20gig%20worker%2C%20who%20has%20to%20contend%20with%20low%20incomes%20and%20the%20burdens%20of%20taking%20on%20loans.%20Workers%20are%20responsible%20for%20costs%20associated%20with%20getting%20their%20own%20vehicles%20or%20modes%20of%20transport%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Uber%20or%20Zomato.%20Even%20maintenance%20and%20fuel%20costs%20are%20accrued%20to%20the%20driver.%20If%20the%20worker%20is%20unable%20to%20raise%20money%20for%20such%20investments%20in%20cars%20or%20bikes%2C%20they%20end%20up%20taking%20on%20a%20loan%20which%20adds%20to%20their%20financial%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Furban-company-workers-protest-job-losses-after-blocked-ids-unrealistic-rating-requirements%5C%22%3EUrban%20Company%20Workers%20Protest%20Job%20Losses%20After%20Blocked%20IDs%2C%20%E2%80%98Unrealistic%E2%80%99%20Rating%20Requirements%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20tackle%20such%20issues%2C%20workers%20have%20also%20got%20into%20financial%20arrangements%20that%20take%20care%20of%20the%20burden%20of%20investment%20but%20cut%20into%20their%20shares%20of%20income.%20Gowada%2C%20an%20Uber%20driver%2C%20was%20one%20such%20case.%20Without%20having%20the%20financial%20means%20to%20get%20hold%20of%20a%20car%2C%20he%20instead%20has%20opted%20for%20a%20person%2C%20who%20bought%20a%20slew%20of%20commercial%20vehicles%2C%20to%20work%20under%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20Rs%20100%20cab%20ride%2C%20after%20cutting%20the%20commission%20of%20both%20Uber%20and%20the%20contractor%2C%20Gowada%20ends%20up%20pocketing%20only%20Rs%2030.%20Describing%20working%2C%20sometimes%2016%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20he%20contends%20with%20the%20situation%20he%20finds%20himself%20in.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20is%20strenuous%2C%20the%20sahebji%20takes%20care%20of%20our%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20describes%20Gowada%2C%20having%20stayed%20up%20for%20the%20last%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20slow-moving%20needle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGowada%20is%20among%20many%20who%20dream%20of%20owning%20their%20own%20cars.%20If%20this%20idea%20is%20not%20apparent%2C%20it%20is%20made%20so%20by%20plastering%20this%20message%20in%20apps%20like%20Uber%20as%20soon%20as%20one%20gets%20to%20know%20of%20their%20ride%20details.%20While%20putting%20this%20message%20across%20to%20the%20consumer%2C%20it%20almost%20appears%20to%20pass%20the%20responsibility%20as%20well.%20In%20lacking%20any%20support%20from%20the%20employer%2C%20their%20interactions%20with%20other%20workers%20are%20limited%20to%20high%20traffic%20areas%20like%20malls%20or%20on%20social%20media%20such%20as%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20spaces%20have%20provided%20sites%20for%20airing%20grievances%20and%20organising%20movements%2C%20which%20have%20spilled%20over%20to%20real%20organised%20movements%20such%20as%20the%20All%20India%20Gig%20Workers%20Union.%20Such%20movements%20have%20raised%20demands%20of%20their%20local%20leaders%20to%20improve%20the%20conditions%20and%20recognition%20of%20the%20gig%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20effect%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Feconomy%2F2023%2F7%2F27%2Findian-states-new-tax-on-digital-platforms-sets-gig-workers-against-firms%5C%22%3Erecently%20passed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Platform-Based%20Gig%20Workers%20(Registration%20and%20Welfare)%20Act%20that%20grants%20workers%20social%20security%20benefits%20like%20accident%20and%20health%20insurance%2C%20pension%20and%20a%20revenue-based%20tax%20on%20the%20platforms%20and%20aggregators%20to%20be%20contributed%20to%20an%20employee%20welfare%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20laws%20are%20also%20being%20considered%20in%20states%20like%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fkarnataka-budget-gig-workers-to-get-free-life-insurance-cover-8810408%2F%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20accidental%20insurance%20coverage%20of%20gig%20workers.%20Advancements%20are%20also%20being%20made%20closer%20to%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20where%20the%20Labour%20Department%20of%20Haryana%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faigwu_union%2Fstatus%2F1690012355525050369%5C%22%3Erecognised%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20status%20of%20Urban%20Company%20workers%20as%20employees%20and%20thus%20entitled%20to%20social%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20clarifications%20of%20the%20legal%20definition%20and%20protection%20of%20gig%20workers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-plans-welfare-measures-gig-workers-ahead-elections-2023-08-11%2F%5C%22%3Eyet%20to%20come%20into%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20such%20efforts%20from%20the%20state-level%20will%20only%20put%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20gig%20worker%20to%20be%20recognised%20soon%2C%20especially%20with%20general%20elections%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20commentary%20is%20penned%20down%20from%20the%20documented%20findings%20of%20a%20recent%20Azaad%20Awaaz%20edition.%20Click%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fazaadawaazcnes.wordpress.com%2F2023%2F07%2F12%2Fthe-gig-economy-in-india-unveiling-the-exploitation-of-workers%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20access%20the%20edition%20on%20The%20Gig%20Economy%E2%80%A6%20Azaad%20Awaaz%2C%20an%20initiative%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University%2C%20which%20works%20on%20issues%20of%20social%20exclusion%2C%20marginalisation%2C%20and%20discrimination%20experienced%20by%20vulnerable%2C%20precarious%20communities%20across%20India.%20To%20review%20its%20work%20and%20patrika%20(magazine)%2C%20please%20see%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fazaadawaazcnes.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp