re%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20hill-majority%20Kukis%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20protest%20by%20the%20Chin-Kuki%20tribes%20against%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20inclusion%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20category%20has%20now%20changed%20into%20a%20demand%20by%20the%20Kukis%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bseparate%20administration%26quot%3B%2C%20whatever%20that%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20it%20taking%20so%20long%20for%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20to%20completely%20stop%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20could%20be%20five%20major%20reasons%20behind%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENarcoterrorism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20narcoterrorism%20and%20drug%20cartels%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%20Worldometer%2C%20the%20real-time%20statistics%20website%20that%20shot%20to%20fame%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20reported%20that%20drug%20trafficking%2C%20poppy%20cultivation%20and%20heroin%20business%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20%24110%20billion%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20located%20right%20between%20the%20top%20two%20biggest%20opium%20producers%20-%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20the%20'Golden%20Triangle'%20(Myanmar%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Laos).%20India's%20western%20border%20is%20well%20protected%20due%20to%20the%20active%20threat%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20the%20eastern%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20remains%20largely%20unprotected%20as%20of%20date%2C%20making%20it%20the%20preferred%20route%20for%20drug%20cartels%20to%20move%20their%20'product'.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEastern%20Manipur's%20five%20districts%20share%20a%20400-km%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20and%20less%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20international%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20is%20fenced%2C%20leaving%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkuki-chin-poppy-cultivation-the-role-of-a-plant-in-manipur-ethnic-violence-4085961%5C%22%3Eregion%20wide%20open%20for%20drug%20smuggling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20total%20length%20of%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%20is%201%2C600%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fvu1tfrs_myanmar-poppy-fields_625x300_01_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EPoppy%20farms%20in%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State's%20northern%20tip%20are%20just%2060%20km%20from%20Manipur's%20border%20town%20Moreh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20alarming%20reason%20to%20expedite%20border-fencing%2C%20Myanmar%20being%20a%20friendly%20nation.%20But%20India's%20insurgency%20hub%20is%20also%20in%20this%20very%20region.%20So%20the%20question%20is%2C%20have%20we%20taken%20this%20lightly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shifting%20of%20the%20'Golden%20Triangle'%20is%20well-documented%20with%20large-scale%20opium%20cultivation%20mushrooming%20in%20Manipur.%20Media%20reports%20have%20indicated%20at%20the%20direct%20involvement%20of%20Myanmar%20drug%20cartels.%20Over%2018%2C000%20acres%20of%20opium%20cultivation%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20which%20were%20in%20Chin-Kuki%20dominated%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManipur's%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%20arrested%20over%20a%20thousand%20people%20in%20drugs%20cases%20following%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20zero-tolerance%20to%20drugs%20policy.%20All%20these%20factors%20strengthen%20the%20allegation%20that%20narcotics%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20behind%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstability%20In%20Myanmar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20instability%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar%20where%20a%20military%20junta%20government%20is%20running%20the%20show%20has%20forced%20many%20of%20its%20citizens%20to%20flee%20to%20India.%20Armed%20rebellion%2C%20junta%20crackdowns%20and%20airstrikes%20on%20anti-junta%20forces%20are%20happening%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20United%20Nations%20report%20on%20March%206%20this%20year%20-%20nearly%20two%20months%20before%20ethnic%20clashes%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20-%20estimated%20Myanmar's%20internally%20displaced%20people%20at%2017%20lakh%2C%20of%20which%2010.8%20lakh%20were%20refugees%20and%20asylum-seekers.%20The%2016-km%20'free%20movement%20region'%20policy%20between%20India%20and%20Myanmar%20also%20eases%20entry%20of%20refugees%20into%20Manipur%20via%20the%20border%20trading%20town%20of%20Moreh.%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20insurgents%20in%20Myanmar's%20western%20region%20bordering%20India%20are%20present%20predominantly%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fquestions-raised-after-over-700-myanmar-nationals-enter-manipur-in-2-days-4238261%5C%22%3EIndia%20is%20not%20a%20signatory%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Refugee%20Convention%2C%201951%2C%20and%20its%201967%20protocol%2C%20yet%20Mizoram%20has%20been%20openly%20welcoming%20Myanmar%20refugees%2C%20up%20to%2040%2C000%20of%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20state%20home%20department%20data.%20Mizoram%20also%20registers%20them%20formally%20as%20%26quot%3Brefugees%26quot%3B%2C%20who%20may%20be%20deported%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F8g8in3eg_myanmar-illegal-manipur_625x300_29_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20said%20narcoterrorists%20and%20illegal%20Myanmar%20immigrants%20are%20behind%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20neighbouring%20Manipur%2C%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20some%20steps%20to%20provide%20humanitarian%20help%20to%20the%20refugees%20whose%20actual%20number%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20ascertained.%20But%20the%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20community%20allegedly%20do%20not%20ascribe%20refugee%20status%20to%20those%20who%20fled%20from%20Myanmar%20as%20they%20belong%20to%20the%20same%20ethnic%20groups%2C%20which%20the%20Meiteis%20allege%20shows%20ethnicity%20being%20given%20preference%20over%20nationality.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20those%20seeking%20asylum%20prefer%20Manipur%2C%20for%20they%20would%20not%20be%20labelled%20as%20refugees%20and%20denied%20the%20same%20support%20that%20Indian%20citizens%20get.%20Many%20Myanmar%20citizens%20having%20fake%20Aadhaar%20and%20other%20documents%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColonial%20Divide%20And%20Rule%20Lingering%20Effects%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20a%20master%20stroke%20by%20the%20British%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-balkanisation-on-ethnic-lines-union-minister-rajkumar-ranjan-singh-writes-to-pm-narendra-modi-on-manipur-4053841%5C%22%3Eenabled%20them%20to%20control%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20zamindari%20system%2C%20a%20form%20of%20'divide%20and%20rule'.%20Under%20the%20pretext%20of%20protecting%20the%20Manipur%20kingdom%20from%20Burma%2C%20the%20British%20started%20resettling%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20people%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20Manipur%20and%20introduced%20the%20feudal%20system%2C%20particularly%20chieftainship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20British%20left%2C%20India%20passed%20the%20Zamindari%20Abolition%20Act%2C%201951%2C%20and%20ended%20the%20zamindari%20system%2C%20but%20in%20Manipur%20the%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20still%20practice%20it.%20Even%20the%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20dominated%20state%20Mizoram%20scrapped%20chieftainship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chiefs%20in%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20villages%20in%20Manipur%20are%20the%20sole%20leaders%20of%20their%20settlements%20and%20own%20entire%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feudal%20system%20follows%20nepotism%20and%20autocracy%20-%20when%20the%20current%20chief%20dies%2C%20only%20his%20son%20can%20become%20the%20next%20chief.%20The%20hunger%20for%20power%20and%20disloyalty%20among%20siblings%20have%20led%20to%20mushrooming%20of%20many%20villages%20in%20Manipur%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20areas%20dominated%20by%20them.%20They%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20carrying%20out%20massive%20deforestation%20as%20the%20new%20villages%20are%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20forest%20areas.%20With%20Myanmar%20refugees%20and%20illegal%20immigrants%20pouring%20into%20Manipur%2C%20setting%20up%20new%20villages%20becomes%20easier%20as%20the%20newcomers%20could%20live%20as%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F2v4hsppg_manipur-violence-_625x300_05_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%20forest%20department%20beat%20office%20that%20was%20set%20on%20fire%20in%20Churachandpur%20(File)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%20in%20a%20report%20on%20June%206%2C%202022%2C%20said%20Manipur%20has%20some%20934%20unrecognised%20villages.%20The%20Manipur%20government%20had%20been%20carrying%20out%20eviction%20drives%20to%20reclaim%20forest%20lands%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20leading%20to%20violent%20protests%20at%20times.%20The%20forest%20department's%20offices%20in%20Churachandpur%20district%20were%20the%20first%20to%20be%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20miscreants%20before%20large-scale%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20May%203%20evening.%20One%20of%20the%20offices%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolice-case-fir-filed-against-4-over-editors-guild-of-india-crowdfunded-manipur-report-4357115%5C%22%3Emisidentified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BKuki%20house%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Editor's%20Guild%20of%20India%20in%20its%20recent%20report%20on%20the%20media's%20coverage%20of%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%20The%20guild%20later%20corrected%20the%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestionable%20Agreement%20With%20Insurgents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20insurgents%20from%20nearly%2025%20armed%20groups%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faerial-pics-of-manipur-insurgent-camps-as-army-conducts-surprise-checks-4088722%5C%22%3Eunder%20intense%20scrutiny%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20allegedly%20participating%20in%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20despite%20signing%20a%20tripartite%20peace%20agreement%20in%202008%20with%20the%20centre%2C%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20military%2C%20called%20the%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20Asian%20Terrorism%20Portal%2C%20a%20repository%20of%20terrorism%20incidents%2C%20has%20recorded%20extortion%20from%20common%20people%20and%20commercial%20drivers%20on%20highways%2C%20kidnappings%2C%20and%20other%20illegal%20activities%20by%20the%20insurgents%20even%20after%20signing%20the%20SoO%20agreement.%20There%20are%20records%20of%20signed%20'memos'%20sent%20by%20leaders%20of%20some%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20citing%20violation%20of%20SoO%20agreement%20ground%20rules%20by%20another%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fq6v4eko_manipur-insurgent-camp-soo_625x300_02_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20has%20been%20conducting%20surprise%20checks%20on%20'suspension%20of%20operations'%20(SoO)%20camps%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Churachandpur%2C%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20violence%20that%20started%20on%20May%203%2C%20visuals%20from%20a%20rally%20show%20people%2C%20allegedly%20from%20the%20SoO%20groups%2C%20in%20camouflage%20battledress%20carrying%20assault%20rifles.%20An%20insurgent%20group%20that%20had%20signed%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20had%20also%20made%20a%20call%20to%20end%20a%20two-month-long%20blockade%20of%20a%20National%20Highway.%20The%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20is%20questionable%20if%20the%20insurgent%20groups%20are%20carrying%20out%20illegal%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInadequate%20Constitutional%20Protection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20the%20constitutional%20protection%20given%20to%20ethnic%20groups%20in%20India's%20north-east%20seems%20to%20be%20inadequate%20to%20cover%20today's%20realities.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20has%20been%20over%2076%20years%20since%20Independence.%20It%20cannot%20be%20denied%20the%20north-east%20saw%20slow%20growth%20compared%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20until%20development%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20past%20nine%20years.%20The%20people%20in%20the%20north-east%20are%20ethnically%20and%20culturally%20diverse%2C%20distinct%20with%20their%20own%20customs%20and%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20major%20ethnic%20groups%20in%20every%20state%20in%20the%20north-east%20are%20protected%20by%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989.%20The%20Mizos%20in%20Mizoram%3B%20the%20Khasi%2C%20Jantia%2C%20and%20Garo%20in%20Meghalaya%3B%20Nagas%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20major%20indigenous%20ethnic%20groups%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Assam%2C%20Tripura%20and%20Sikkim%20are%20protected%20by%20this%20important%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Manipur%2C%20only%20the%20Nagas%20and%20Kukis%20are%20protected.%20The%20Meiteis%2C%20who%20are%20also%20a%20major%20ethnic%20group%20in%20Manipur%2C%20are%20not%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20exclusion%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20discrimination%20against%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20Without%20protection%20under%20the%20law%2C%20the%20Meitei%20community%20is%20left%20with%20access%20to%20a%20mere%206-8%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20land%20area%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20is%20confined%20to%20the%20valley%20region.%20This%20is%20the%20actual%20area%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fhow-to-misread-ethnic-violence-in-manipur-4017904%5C%22%3EMeiteis%20can%20live%2C%20own%20land%2C%20and%20call%20it%20their%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20the%20other%2092-94%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20state%20is%20denied%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recognised%20tribes%20can%2C%20however%2C%20own%20land%20and%20live%20in%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5gl7kf2g_manipur-generic-debanish-credit_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMeiteis%20cannot%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%2C%20while%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20can%20own%20land%20and%20property%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reservation%20system%2C%20which%20is%2031%20per%20cent%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20in%20Manipur%2C%20has%20not%20been%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Meiteis.%20With%20similar%20opportunities%20being%20provided%2C%20the%20representation%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20in%20jobs%20and%20education%20has%20been%20declining.%20Data%20from%20the%20last%20two%20results%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20shows%20many%20ST%20candidates%20from%20the%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20have%20been%20selected%20on%20merit%20plus%20the%2031%20per%20cent%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%20have%20migrated%20to%20other%20cities%20in%20the%20struggle%20to%20support%20themselves%20and%20their%20families%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20opportunity%20and%20support%20in%20their%20own%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20British%20Census%20reports%20in%201901%20recorded%20the%20Meiteis%20as%20%26quot%3Btribes%26quot%3B.%20Shockingly%2C%20this%20disappeared%20from%20the%20same%20list%20after%20Independence.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20explanation%20and%20consensus%20on%20how%20the%20vanishing%20act%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20these%20five%20factors%20are%20interconnected%2C%20so%20one%20solution%20may%20not%20fit%20all.%20What%20is%20certain%20is%20decisive%20action%20is%20the%20only%20way%20forward.%20At%20the%20very%20least%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20need%20constitutional%20protection%20against%20all%20these%20factors%20and%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20not%20asking%20for%20extra%20cushioning%2C%20but%20to%20be%20treated%20and%20protected%20just%20as%20other%20tribes%20in%20the%20north-east.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Debanish%20Achom%20is%20Editor%2C%20News%2C%20at%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694701200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fec1496o8_manipur-violence_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2F5-reasons-why-manipur-crisis-is-solvable-not-4387040%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20is%20far%20from%20over%2C%20four%20months%20since%20it%20started.%20Reports%20of%20gunfights%20and%20deaths%20come%20almost%20every%20day.%20The%20security%20forces%20have%20set%20up%20safe%20zones%2C%20dividing%20areas%20where%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis%20live.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2F5-reasons-why-manipur-crisis-is-solvable-not-4387040%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2F5-reasons-why-manipur-crisis-is-solvable-not-4387040%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2F5-reasons-why-manipur-crisis-is-solvable-not-4387040%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lawyer%20Sends%20%26quot%3BUnprepared%26quot%3B%20Junior%20To%20Supreme%20Court.%20What%20Happened%20Next%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20slapped%20Rs%202%2C000%20as%20costs%20on%20an%20advocate%20on%20record%20for%20sending%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprepared%26quot%3B%20junior%20to%20court%20in%20his%20place%20to%20seek%20an%20adjournment.%20The%20advocate%20on%20record%20is%20a%20lawyer%20authorised%20to%20represent%20clients%20and%20file%20cases%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20took%20up%20the%20matter%20listed%20for%20hearing%2C%20a%20junior%20lawyer%20appeared%20and%20requested%20the%20matter%20be%20deferred%20as%20the%20main%20advocate%20was%20not%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20take%20us%20for%20granted%20like%20this.%20There%20are%20infrastructural%20costs%20involved%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20court.%20Start%20arguing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20PS%20Narasimha%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20lawyer%20told%20the%20bench%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20case%20and%20had%20no%20instructions%20to%20argue%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20exception%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20under%20instructions%20to%20hear%20the%20case%20from%20the%20Constitution.%20Please%20call%20the%20advocate%20on%20record.%20Ask%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20us.%26quot%3B%20Later%2C%20the%20advocate%20on%20record%20appeared%20through%20video%20conferencing%20and%20apologised%20to%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20sent%20a%20junior%20to%20the%20court%20without%20any%20paper%20and%20knowledge%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20recorded%20in%20its%20order%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20junior%20was%20sent%20unprepared%20without%20any%20papers.%20When%20we%20declined%20to%20grant%20an%20adjournment%2C%20the%20advocate%20on%20record%20appeared.%20Matters%20cannot%20be%20conducted%20in%20this%20manner.%20This%20is%20doing%20a%20disservice%20to%20both%20the%20court%20and%20to%20the%20junior%20who%20is%20made%20to%20appear%20without%20any%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3