r%2014%2C%20%E2%80%93%20attributed%20the%20responsibility%20for%20transforming%20Delhi%20from%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20greenest%20capital%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20polluted%20capital%20to%20both%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovely%20has%20been%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20president%20in%20the%20past.%20He%20was%20also%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Sheila%20Dikshit%20government%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20appointed%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief%20on%20August%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovely%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Delhi%20unit%20will%20follow%20the%20party%20high%20command%20on%20any%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20but%20will%20not%20%E2%80%9Ccompromise%20on%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20interests%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDelhi%20was%20the%20greenest%20capital%20in%20the%20world%20and%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20was%20talked%20about%20everywhere.%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20ministers%20were%20called%20to%20even%20cities%20such%20as%20Copenhagen%20to%20discuss%20how%20Delhi%20was%20made%20the%20greenest%20capital.%20But%20in%20seven%20years%2C%20Delhi%20has%20gone%20from%20the%20greenest%20capital%20to%20become%20the%20most%20polluted%20capital.%20Both%20these%20parties%20are%20responsible%20for%20that.%20So%2C%20how%20can%20I%20stop%20myself%20from%20speaking%20against%20both%20of%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20there%20will%20be%20an%20issue%20pertaining%20to%20development%20and%20welfare%20of%20Delhi%20we%20will%20speak%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovely%20was%20speaking%20at%20an%20event%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20headquarters%20in%20Rouse%20Avenue.%20Several%20top%20Delhi%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20including%20Ajay%20Maken%2C%20Alka%20Lamba%2C%20Sandeep%20Dikshit%2C%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20Udit%20Raj%2C%20among%20others%2C%20were%20present%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20came%20just%20a%20day%20after%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%20on%20Wednesday%20(September%2013)%20at%20their%20first%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-to-boycott-tv-shows-that-conduct-inflammatory-debates%5C%22%3Econclude%20seat-sharing%20talks%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelhi%20has%20seen%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famid-disagreements-over-state-polls-congress-and-aap-say-india-alliance-is-for-national-election%5C%22%3E%20disagreements%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20members%20%E2%80%93%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurmurs%20of%20fissures%20emerged%20after%20Delhi%20Congress%20leader%20Alka%20Lamba%20said%20on%20August%2016%2C%20after%20a%20party%20organisational%20meeting%2C%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20contest%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20drew%20sharp%20reactions%20from%20AAP%2C%20and%20there%20were%20speculations%20over%20whether%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20and%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20national%20convener%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20would%20attend%20the%20India%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20Mumbai%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20clarifications%20were%20issued%2C%20Kejriwal%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20attend%20the%20grouping%E2%80%99s%20third%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famid-disagreements-over-state-polls-congress-and-aap-say-india-alliance-is-for-national-election%5C%22%3EAmid%20Disagreements%20Over%20State%20Polls%2C%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20Say%20India%20Alliance%20Is%20for%20%E2%80%98National%E2%80%99%20Election%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20that%2C%20AAP%20had%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-second-opposition-meet-delhi-ordinance-issue-still-divides-aap-and-congress%5C%22%3Ejoined%20the%20second%20INDIA%20bloc%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%2C%20after%20the%20Congress%20publicly%20promised%20to%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-second-opposition-meet-congress-says-it-will-not-support-delhi-ordinance%5C%22%3Esupport%20the%20contentious%20Delhi%20ordinance%20on%20control%20of%20services%20in%20parliament%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-services-bill-rajya-sabha-arvind-kejriwal-centre-ias-officer-amit-shah%5C%22%3Elaw%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rift%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20over%20the%20Delhi%20ordinance%20had%20also%20dominated%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpatna-amidst-aap-congress-sparring-16-opposition-parties-vow-to-unitedly-fight-the-bjp%5C%22%3Efirst%20INDIA%20alliance%20meeting%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovely%20said%20that%20as%20the%20new%20Delhi%20Congress%20president%2C%20his%20role%20is%20not%20to%20work%20with%20other%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20role%20is%20not%20to%20work%20with%20other%20parties%2C%20my%20role%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Congress%20organisation.%20That%20(working%20with%20other%20parties)%20is%20the%20role%20of%20the%20leadership%20and%20whatever%20their%20direction%20will%20be%20we%20will%20follow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20statements%20made%20by%20Lamba%20and%20the%20ensuing%20differences%20with%20AAP%2C%20Lovely%20said%20that%20he%20stands%20by%20the%20leaders%20who%20aired%20their%20views%20freely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20difference%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20is%20that%20we%20are%20allowed%20to%20express%20our%20views%20freely.%20Everyone%20can%20express%20their%20views%20freely%20and%20I%20stand%20by%20those%20leaders%20as%20they%20have%20every%20right%20to%20speak%20freely.%20The%20Congress%20is%20a%20disciplined%20party%2C%20and%20when%20the%20high%20command%20asked%20for%20our%20views%2C%20some%20were%20in%20support%20of%20it%20and%20some%20were%20against.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20everyone%20said%20that%20these%20are%20our%20views%20and%20whatever%20decision%20the%20high%20command%20takes%2C%20we%20will%20abide%20by%20that.%20So%2C%20there%20are%20no%20issues%20and%20the%20decisions%20(related%20to%20seat%20sharing)%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20high%20command.%20But%20my%20duty%20as%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Congress%20and%20make%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20ready%20for%20any%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20Lovely%E2%80%99s%20second%20run%20as%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20president.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20step%20down%20from%20his%20post%20in%202015.%20In%20May%202017%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Farvinder-singh-lovely-returns-to-congress-says-he-was-misfit-in-bjp%2Fstory-3v9ICOMOC9J7rRVxUYB0fL.html%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20his%20decision%20to%20leave%20the%20party%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20event%20earlier%2C%20Lovely%20said%20that%20he%20had%20made%20a%20mistake%20which%20he%20continues%20to%20regret%2C%20and%20urged%20those%20who%20have%20left%20the%20Congress%20to%20return%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20appealed%20to%20those%20workers%20who%20have%20become%20annoyed%20with%20us%20to%20return%20because%20their%20DNA%20is%20%5Bof%20the%5D%20Congress%2C%20which%20means%20for%20generations%20they%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Congress%20%5Bparty%5D%20and%20they%20are%20now%20feeling%20suffocated%20in%20other%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20the%20fight%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20started%20is%20not%20only%20a%20fight%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fight%20to%20save%20this%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20India%20have%20to%20decide%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20build%20the%20leadership%20of%20one%20leader%20or%20the%20nation.%20That%20is%20why%20I%E2%80%99ve%20appealed%20to%20all%20Congress%20leaders%20that%20come%20and%20join%20us%20in%20the%20fight%20to%20save%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694700032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FLovely_Rahul-Gandhi_PTI.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-bjp-responsible-for-making-delhi-the-most-polluted-capital-congresss-arvinder-singh-lovely%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Delhi%20was%20the%20greenest%20capital%20in%20the%20world%20and%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20was%20talked%20about%20everywhere.%20But%20in%20seven%20years%2C%20Delhi%20has%20gone%20from%20the%20greenest%20capital%20to%20become%20the%20most%20polluted%20capital%2C'%20said%20Lovely%2C%20who%20has%20assumed%20charge%20as%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-bjp-responsible-for-making-delhi-the-most-polluted-capital-congresss-arvinder-singh-lovely%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20talents%20of%20Ayushmann%20other%20than%20acting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694700000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103667835%2Cimgsize-62560.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2F5-things-ayushmann-khurrana-does-beautifully-apart-from