%2C%20any%20economic%20model%2C%20the%20smallest%20of%20the%20smallest%2C%20even%20nano%20model%2C%20every%20car%20will%20have%20six%20airbags.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20clear%20why%20the%20government%20took%20a%20U-turn%2C%20not%20making%20the%20installation%20of%20six%20airbags%20mandatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20leading%20car%20manufacturer%20told%20the%20business%20daily%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20most%20passenger%20cars%2C%20especially%20those%20priced%20Rs%208%20lakh%20and%20above%2C%20come%20with%20six%20airbags%20as%20standard%20now%2C%20and%20they%20will%20also%20do%20the%20same%20for%20future%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20safety%20point%20of%20view%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20features%20are%20getting%20added%2C%20and%20getting%20six%20airbags%20as%20standard%20has%20become%20a%20norm%20for%20us%20now.%20The%20passenger%20cars%20come%20with%20an%20occupant%20detection%20system%2C%20and%20also%20a%20three-point%20seatbelt%20for%20the%20middle%20passenger%20at%20the%20rear%20seat%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20official%20with%20a%20leading%20company%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20such%20as%20Hyundai%20Motor%20India%20recently%20launched%20its%20Exter%20small%20SUV%20with%20six%20airbags%20as%20standard%2C%20and%20its%20small%20car%20Grand%20i10%20Nios%20also%20comes%20with%20four%20airbags%20as%20standard%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20decisions%20assume%20significance%20in%20a%20country%20that%20has%20the%20deadliest%20roads%20in%20the%20world.%20Poor%20conditions%2C%20lax%20enforcement%2C%20unsafe%20vehicles%20and%20stray%20animals%20lead%20to%20more%20than%20900%2C000%20deaths%20and%20injuries%20a%20year%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2023-05-24%2Ffour-problems-and-solutions-for-india-s-dangerous-roads%5C%22%3Ereported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESafety%20audits%20of%20road%20designs%20before%20starting%2