lls%20of%20terrorists%20including%20Hizbul%20Mujahideen%20poster%20boy%20Burhan%20Wani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECol%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20six-year-old%20son%20and%20a%20two-year-old%20daughter%2C%20was%20a%20combat%20veteran%20and%20was%20awarded%20Sena%20Medal%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20second-in-command%20of%20the%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%2C%20a%20battalion%20tasked%20with%20ensuring%20security%20in%20South%20Anantnag%2C%20Kokernag%20and%20Verinag%20Achabal%20including%20its%20higher%20reaches%2C%20which%20have%20been%20highly%20infested%20with%20terrorists%20especially%20foreign%20mercenaries%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECol%20Singh%20who%20was%20in%20his%20early%2040s%2C%20along%20with%20Major%20Aashish%20Dhonchak%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20Humayun%20Bhat%20and%20one%20soldier%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20encounter%20with%20terrorists%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Kokernag.%20One%20soldier%20is%20still%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20Dhonchak%2C%2034%2C%20who%20had%20a%20close%20brush%20with%20death%20only%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20is%20remembered%20as%20an%20enthusiastic%20officer%20who%20used%20to%20go%20into%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20every%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20promotion%20in%202021%20as%20a%20Colonel%2C%20Singh%20was%20given%20a%20choice%20to%20opt%20for%20peace%20area%20posting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Sir%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20be%20posted%20in%20my%2019%20RR%20(Rashtriya%20Rifles)%20and%20be%20with%20my%20own%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20his%20prompt%20response%2C%20politely%20rejecting%20the%20offer%20that%20had%20been%20made%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECol%20Singh%20always%20wanted%20to%20lead%20from%20the%20front%20and%20the%20reason%20generally%20given%20by%20him%20was%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20one%20under%20my%20command%20is%20safe.%26quot%3B%20A%20sports%20enthusiast%2C%20Col%20Singh%20always%20believed%20in%20uplift%20of%20youth%20and%20engaged%20them%20in%20sports%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E'Chinar%20Cricket%20tournament'%20for%20women%20and%20volleyball%20events%20were%20quite%20frequent%20in%20otherwise%20restive%20areas%20of%20Larkipora%2C%20where%20the%20formation's%20headquarters%20was%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20sports%20lovers%20in%20the%20area%20said%20they%20could%20not%20believe%20that%20Col%20Singh%20was%20no%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%20said%20the%20officer%20was%20always%20available%20for%20youths%20and%20had%20encouraged%20them%20to%20build%20a%20comprehensive%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20believed%20that%20sports%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20building%20a%20society...There%20were%20many%20drug%20addicts%20whom%20he%20sent%20for%20rehabilitation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20woman%20cricketer%20Rubbiya%20Sayeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2010%2C%20Major%20Dhonchak%20and%20his%20team%20were%20participating%20in%20a%20cordon%20and%20search%20operation%20in%20the%20Athlan%20Gadole%20area%20of%20Kokernag%20when%20terrorists%20threw%20a%20grenade%20injuring%20three%20people%20including%20a%20soldier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20time%20he%20ran%20out%20of%20luck...%2C%26quot%3B%20recalls%20one%20of%20the%20officers%20known%20to%20the%20fallen%20soldier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20Dhonchak%20was%20awarded%20with%20Sena%20Medal%20only%20last%20month%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20Independence%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694697120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fnr22oooo_col-manpreet-singh_650x400_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-colonel-manpreet-singh-killed-in-action-was-offered-a-peace-posting-he-refused-kashmir-enco