dentified%20as%20a%20Meitei%20organisation%20and%2C%20certainly%2C%20the%20accusations%20and%20charges%20they%20face%20are%20of%20obstructing%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%2C%20even%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20release%20Meitei%20militants%20accused%20of%20killing%20army%20soldiers%20in%20an%20ambush%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20interviewed%20one%20of%20the%20rising%20leaders%20of%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%2C%20Aheibam%20Chanthoisana%20Chanu%2C%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20organisation%20and%20especially%2C%20its%20growing%20distrust%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%20We%20ask%20how%20this%20distrust%20emerged%20and%20why%20it%20has%20increased%20over%20the%20decades.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Chanu%20is%20asked%20about%20the%20accusations%20and%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20against%20the%20Meira%20Paibi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20she%20is%20asked%20whether%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%20has%20been%20misunderstood%20outside%20Manipur%20and%2C%20perhaps%2C%20misrepresented%20by%20the%20press.%20Are%20they%20victims%20of%20what%20they%20consider%20bad%20journalism%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3RKB6MtwgIQ%3Fsi%3DSgW46_lmFloAprs8%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694696914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14183724%2Fimage-1314.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-manipur-why-the-meira-paibi-a-meitei-womens-collective-distrust-the-assam-rifles%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20their%20early%20years%2C%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%20fought%20against%20alcoholism.%20In%20the%201980s%2C%20they%20struggled%20to%20get%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act%20revoked%20in%20Manipur.%20Now%20they%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20struggle%20between%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-manipur-why-the-meira-paibi-a-meitei-womens-collective-distrust-the-assam-rifles%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHousehold%20Work's%20Burden%20Should%20Be%20Borne%20Equally%20By%20Husband%2C%20Wife%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20modern%20society%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20household%20responsibilities%20should%20be%20borne%20equally%20by%20husband%20and%20wife%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Nitin%20Sambre%20and%20Sharmila%20Deshmukh%20made%20the%20observation%20on%20September%206%20while%20dismissing%20an%20appeal%20filed%20by%20a%2035-year-old%20man%20seeking%20the%20dissolution%20of%20his%2013-year-old%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20not%20establish%20his%20claim%20of%20'cruelty'%20against%20his%20estranged%20wife%2C%20the%20judges%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20had%20challenged%20a%20March%202018%20order%20of%20a%20family%20court%20dismissing%20his%20plea%20seeking%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20got%20married%20in%202010.%20The%20man%20contended%20in%20the%20plea%20that%20his%20wife%20was%20always%20on%20the%20phone%20with%20her%20mother%20and%20did%20not%20do%20household%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20do%20all%20the%20household%20work%20after%20returning%20from%20office%2C%20and%20faced%20abuse%20when%20she%20contacted%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20claimed%20that%20her%20estranged%20husband%20had%20physically%20abused%20her%20on%20several%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20in%20its%20order%2C%20noted%20that%20both%20the%20man%20and%20woman%20were%20employed%2C%20and%20expecting%20the%20wife%20to%20do%20all%20the%20household%20work%20reflects%20a%20regressive%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20modern%20society%20the%20burden%20of%20household%20responsibilities%20have%20to%20be%20borne%20by%20both%20husband%20and%20wife%20equally.%20The%20primitive%20mindset%20expecting%20the%20woman%20of%20the%20house%20to%20solely%20shoulder%20the%20household%20responsibilities%20needs%20to%20undergo%20a%20positive%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20marital%20relationship%20must%20not%20lead%20to%20the%20wife%20in%20this%20case%20getting%20isolated%20from%20her%20parents%20and%20she%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20sever%20the%20ties%20with%20her%20parents%2C%20the%20court%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20in%20contact%20with%20one's%20parents%20cannot%20by%20any%20stretch%20of%20imagination%20be%20construed%20as%20inflicting%20mental%20agony%20on%20the%20other%20party.%20In%20our%20view%2C%20putting%20restrictions%20on%20the%20respondent%20to%20curtail%20her%20contact%20with%20her%20parents%2C%20has%20in%20fact%2C%20subjected%20the%20wife%20to%20mental%20cruelty%20apart%20from%20physical%20cruelty%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694696820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F85mh9qus_bombay-high-court-website-photo_625x300_20_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhousehold-works-burden-should-be-borne-equally-by-husband-wife-bombay-high-court-4389995%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20modern%20society%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20household%20responsibilities%20should%20be%20borne%20equally%20by%20husband%20and%20wife%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhousehold-works-burden-should-be-borne-equally-by-husband-wife-bombay-high-court-4389995%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Will%20India's%20Name%20Go%20The%20Way%20Of%20Turkey%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20host%20nation%20of%20this%20year's%20Group%20of%2020%20summit%20has%20two%20official%20names%3A%20India%20and%20Bharat.%20The%20first%20was%20inherited%20from%20the%20country's%20former%20British%20overlords%3B%20the%20other%20derives%20from%20Sanskrit%20and%20emanates%20an%20ancient%20sanctity.%20There%20was%20much%20social%20media%20fluttering%2C%20therefore%2C%20when%20a%20dinner%20invitation%20went%20out%20to%20conference%20guests%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20the%20expected%20and%20globally%20familiar%20appellation.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20prefers%20the%20Sanskrit.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20word%20echoes%20in%20his%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20relatively%20recent%20precedents%20for%20change%20among%20other%20former%20British%20colonies.%20Burma%2C%20Rhodesia%20and%20Ceylon%20are%20now%20officially%20Myanmar%20(1989)%2C%20Zimbabwe%20(1980)%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20(1972)%2C%20respectively.%20Why%20shouldn't%20India%20decide%20which%20name%20it%20prefers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20deterrent%20is%20that%20any%20rebranding%20comes%20late%20in%20India's%20rise%20to%20global%20prominence.%20It%20takes%20some%20work%20to%20make%20things%20stick.%20Zimbabwe%20was%20helped%20by%20the%20the%20association%20of%20its%20former%20name%20with%20white%20minority%20rule.%20I%20still%20run%20into%20people%20who%20call%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Ceylon.%20The%20Burma-to-Myanmar%20is%20so%20recent%20that%20even%20experts%20stumble%20from%20one%20into%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20case%20in%20point%3A%20Last%20year%2C%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20declared%20that%20%26quot%3BTurkey%26quot%3B%20was%20no%20more%20and%20the%20country%20was%20officially%20T%C3%BCrkiye.%20The%20United%20Nations%20said%20fine%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20harder%20to%20get%20English%20speakers%20to%20adopt%20it.%20Their%20word%20for%20the%20country%20has%20been%20in%20use%20since%20Chaucer.%20(Bloomberg%20News%20style%20is%20still%20%26quot%3BTurkey.%26quot%3B)%20Change%20can%20be%20expensive%20and%20complex.%20Turkish%20Airlines%20has%20officially%20become%20%26quot%3BT%C3%BCrk%20Hava%20Yollar%C4%B1%20Anonim%20Ortakl%C4%B1%C4%9F%C4%B1%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20its%20English%20language%20website%20doesn't%20reflect%20that.%20(Its%20international%20code%2C%20though%2C%20is%20now%20THY.)%C2%A0%20The%20fleet%20of%20more%20than%20400%20planes%20don't%20appear%20to%20be%20repainted%20with%20the%20new%20name%20either.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20as%20one%20wag%20on%20X%20pointed%20out%2C%20the%20top-level%20web%20domain%20initials%20it%20would%20expect%20to%20have%20for%20Bharat%20(.bh)%20have%20long%20been%20taken%20by%20Bahrain.%20Referring%20to%20New%20Delhi's%20agglomeration%20with%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20China%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20one%20X-twitterati%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20abbreviation%20of%20BRICS%2C%20if%20India%20renames%20itself%20Bharat%20and%20the%20invited%20countries%20(Argentina%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Iran%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20UAE)%20join%20it%20next%20year%2C%20will%20be%20BARBIECUES.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20some%20X%20commenters%20snark%20that%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20could%20also%20be%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20attempt%20to%20counter-program%20the%20new%20opposition%20coalition%20that%20sports%20the%20acronym%20I.N.D.I.A.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJokes%20are%20easy.%20The%20Turks%20just%20got%20tired%20of%20their%20country%20being%20associated%20with%20the%20gobbling%20bird%20native%20to%20North%20America%2C%20which%20got%20its%20name%20from%20T%C3%BCrkiye%20in%20the%20first%20place%20(because%20both%20were%20exotic%20in%20the%2016th%20century).%20Still%2C%20training%20foreigners%20to%20say%20%26quot%3BTur-kee-YAY%26quot%3B%20(as%20one%20transliteration%20puts%20it)%20can%20sound%20disconcertingly%20cheerful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20issue%20of%20picking%20the%20right%20new%20name.%20In%20India%2C%20there%20is%20local%20competition%20from%20%26quot%3BHindustan%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20its%20own%20sensitivities%2C%20including%20a%20Persian%20origin.%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20has%20etymological%20roots%20in%20the%20Indus%20River%2C%20which%20now%20runs%20mostly%20in%20Pakistan.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20open%20an%20old%20can%20of%20worms%20if%20he%20decides%20to%20ditch%20%26quot%3BIndia.%26quot%3B%20Back%20in%201947%2C%20as%20independence%20approached%2C%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%2C%20founder%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20was%20infuriated%20that%20the%20British%20allowed%20his%20rival%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20to%20keep%20the%20name%20India%2C%20making%20it%20look%20like%20the%20successor%20state%20to%20the%20British%20Raj%20(and%20its%20immense%20territory).%20Could%20Pakistan%20claim%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20if%20its%20neighbor%20becomes%20Bharat%3F%20The%20subcontinent's%20already%20seen%20two%20original%20partitioned%20components%20change%20names%20after%20a%201971%20war%20of%20independence%3A%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan%20were%20once%20East%20Pakistan%20and%20West%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20independence%20and%20separation%20often%20make%20nomenclature%20a%20very%20testy%20affair.%20In%20Africa%2C%20postcolonial%20referendums%20helped%20settle%20the%20names%20of%20the%20French%20and%20Belgian%20Congos%2C%20which%20became%20the%20Republic%20of%20Congo%20and%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo.%20The%20latter%20was%2C%20for%20many%20years%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Zaire.%20North%20and%20South%20Korea%20refer%20to%20themselves%20with%20different%20names%20in%20their%20language%3A%20Choson%20and%20Hanguk%2C%20respectively.%20However%2C%20Pyongyang%20calls%20its%20rival%20South%20Choson%20and%20Seoul%20calls%20its%20neighbor%20North%20Han.%20Greece%20objected%20to%20the%20former%20Yugoslav%20republic%20of%20Macedonia%20retaining%20its%20name%20after%20its%20independence%2C%20claiming%20it%20for%20one%20of%20its%20own%20provinces.%20Athens%20was%20ameliorated%20in%202019%20with%20an%20agreement%20to%20add%20a%20direction%20of%20the%20compass%20to%20the%20new%20republic.%20Still%2C%20the%20North%20Macedonians%20are%20mighty%20annoyed%20at%20the%20extra%20syllable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Philippines%2C%20the%20country%20of%20my%20birth%2C%20has%20struggled%20with%20its%20name%20for%20more%20than%20a%20century.%20It%20comes%20from%20%26quot%3BIslas%20Felipinas%2C%26quot%3B%20conferred%20on%20the%20islands%20by%20explorers%20from%20Spain%20in%20honor%20of%20the%20then%20heir%20to%20the%20throne%20of%20the%20country%3A%20the%20future%20Philip%20II%2C%20who%20would%20send%20that%20armada%20against%20England%20in%201588.%20It's%20an%20ironic%20legacy%20from%20a%20colonial%20power%20that%20oppressed%20the%20archipelago%20for%20300%20years.%20Several%20decades%20ago%2C%20there%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20rename%20the%20country%20%26quot%3BMaharlika%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20pre-Spanish%20word%20denoting%20nobility.%20While%20some%20nationalists%20were%20enthusiastic%2C%20it%20came%20from%20too%20far%20in%20the%20past%20to%20catch%20on.%20Filipinos%20have%20instead%20warmed%20to%20the%20slangy%2C%20slightly%20irreverent%20%26quot%3Bpinoy%26quot%3B%20to%20describe%20themselves.%20Perhaps%20some%20portmanteau%20national%20name%20can%20be%20manufactured%20with%20that%20to%20reflect%20the%20country's%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20maybe%20it%20doesn't%20matter.%20Maybe%20the%20better%20part%20of%20valor%20(and%20value%2C%20if%20you%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20a%20branding%20budget)%20is%20to%20be%20confident%20in%20your%20identity%20and%20to%20live%20with%20the%20name%20you've%20got%20or%20with%20a%20babel%20of%20them.%20The%20Germans%20call%20their%20country%20Deutschland%20but%20the%20Poles%20call%20it%20%26quot%3BNiemcy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20French%20%26quot%3BAllemagne%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chinese%20%26quot%3BD%C3%A9gu%C3%B3%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Danes%20%26quot%3BTyskland.%26quot%3B%20The%20Germans%20(once%20East%20and%20West%20themselves)%20are%20still%20very%20German%20no%20matter%20the%20designation.%20Confoederatio%20Helvetica%20is%20not%20a%20font%20but%20the%20constitutional%20name%20for%20Switzerland%2C%20the%20Latin%20papering%20over%20the%20country's%20four%20official%20languages.%20The%20Alpine%20nation%20isn't%20about%20to%20be%20mistaken%20for%20someplace%20else.%20Even%20Spaniards%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20someone%20from%20Suiza%20and%20people%20from%20Suecia%20(Sweden).%20China%20doesn't%20insist%20on%20being%20called%20Zhongguo%20by%20non-Chinese%20speakers.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20refer%20to%20Japan%20as%20Nihon-koku%20(unless%20you%20want%20to).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20is%2C%20the%20Turks%20have%20always%20called%20their%20country%20T%C3%BCrkiye%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20is%20already%20in%20widespread%20use%20in%20the%20country%20also%20known%20as%20India.%20Those%20names%20can%20coexist%20with%20what%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20uses.%20There's%20no%20need%20to%20force%20universal%20compliance.%20At%20least%20not%20immediately.%20Give%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20time%20to%20come%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20The%20opinions%20expressed%20within%20this%20article%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694696820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F6nuu37j_bharat-pm_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-to-bharat-examining-precedents-and-their-outcomes-4389870%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20host%20nation%20of%20this%20year's%20Group%20of%2020%20summit%20has%20two%20official%20names%3A%20India%20and%20Bharat.%20The%20first%20was%20inherited%20from%20the%20country's%20former%20British%20overlords%3B%20the%20other%20derives%20from%20Sanskrit%20and%20emanates%20an%20ancient%20sanctity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-to-bharat-examining-precedents-and-their-outcomes-4389870%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-to-bharat-examining-precedents-and-their-outcomes-4389870%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-to-bharat-examining-precedents-and-their-outcomes-4389870%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDhoni%2C%20ISRO%20Chief%26quot%3B%3A%20Gavaskar's%20Wish-list%20To%20BCCI%20For%20WC%20'Golden%20Ticket'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20from%20October%205%20to%20November%2019%20across%2010%20venues%20in%20India.%20After%20sharing%20the%20hosting%20rights%20in%201987%2C%201996%20and%202011%2C%20India%20will%20solely%20host%20the%20World%20Cup%20this%20time%20around.%20Before%20the%20tournament%20kicks%20off%20next%20month%2C%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20give%20the%20fans%20the%20best%20possible%20experience.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20BCCI%20has%20launched%20a%20huge%20initiative%20by%20presenting%20'Golden%20Ticket'%20to%20some%20prominent%20names.%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20legendary%20bollywood%20actor%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20became%20the%20first%20person%20to%20receive%20the%20special%20guest%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20days%20later%2C%20BCCI%20Secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20also%20presented%20a%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Ticket%20to%20legendary%20batter%20Sachin%20Tendilkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20India's%20first%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20in%201983%2C%20praised%20BCCI%20for%20the%20initiative%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20hounour%20pioneers%20of%20their%20respective%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gavaskar%20also%20wants%20BCCI%20to%20give%20Golden%20Ticket%20to%20ISRO%20chief%2C%20S.%20Somnath%2C%20under%20whom%20India%20landed%20on%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20also%20hoped%20that%20BCCI%20would%20honour%20two%20World%20Cup-winning%20captains%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kapil%20Dev%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40958-ramlal-nikhanj-kapil-dev-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20also%20naming%20other%20prominent%20athletes%20of%20their%20respective%20fields%20who%20have%20made%20the%20country%20proud%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20by%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20to%20honour%20persons%20who%20have%20done%20yeoman%20service%20in%20their%20respective%20fields%20is%20a%20terrific%20one.%20As%20of%20writing%2C%20the%20one%20and%20only%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20given%20a%20golden%20ticket%20to%20witness%20the%20World%20Cup%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20wrote%20in%20his%20column%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcolumns%2Fonthewriteline-sunil-gavaskar%2Fdhoni-neeraj-chopra-kapil-dev-isro-chief-bcci-golden-ticket-for-icc-cricket-world-cup-bopanna-sharath-kamal%2Farticle67299013.ece%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20known%20how%20many%20others%20are%20on%20the%20list%2C%20but%20hopefully%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20ISRO%2C%20under%20whom%20India%20landed%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20will%20be%20one.%20Obviously%2C%20it%20can't%20be%20given%20to%20everybody%20who%20has%20played%20for%20India%2C%20but%20if%20the%20associations%20where%20the%20matches%20are%20being%20played%20are%20instructed%20to%20invite%20the%20Indian%20players%20from%20their%20city%20to%20the%20games%20in%20that%20city%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20magnificent%20gesture.%20Of%20course%2C%20two%20others%20who%20deserve%20the%20golden%20ticket%20are%20the%20two%20World%20Cup-winning%20captains%2C%20Kapil%20Dev%20and%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni.%20Neeraj%20Chopra%2C%20the%20Olympic%20and%20World%20Athletics%20Championship%20gold%20medallist%2C%20is%20another%20one%20who%20comes%20to%20mind%20for%20the%20BCCI%20golden%20ticket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20these%20people%20can%20attend%20a%20match%20or%20not%20doesn't%20matter.%20It's%20the%20thought%20that%20will%20surely%20be%20appreciated%20by%20the%20recipients.%20It's%20a%20great%20initiative%20that%20is%20seen%20at%20Wimbledon%20and%20the%20US%20Open%20Tennis%2C%20where%20current%20as%20well%20as%20former%20champions%20from%20other%20sports%20are%20special%20invitees%20to%20witness%20the%20tournaments.%20India%20has%20so%20many%20sporting%20heroes%2C%20and%20if%20they%20are%20also%20recognised%20with%20the%20golden%20ticket%2C%20the%20image%20of%20the%20BCCI%20will%20get%20really%20bright.%20Rohan%20Bopanna%2C%20who%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2043%2C%20finished%20runner-up%20at%20the%20US%20Open%20recently%2C%20and%20Sharath%20(Kamal)%20who%20is%20a%20super%20legend%20in%20table%20tennis%2C%20are%20two%20other%20names.%20They%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20games%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20recognition%20that%20matters.%20Well%20done%2C%20BCCI%2C!%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694696820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fepq5ns0o_sunil-gavaskar-afp_625x300_23_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhopefully-ms-dhoni-isro-chief-also-sunil-gavaskar-gives-wish-list-to-bcci-for-world-cup-golden-ticket-recipients-4388861%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20from%20October%205%20to%20November%2019%20across%2010%20venues%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhopefully-ms-dhoni-isro-chief-also-sunil-gavaskar-gives-wish-list-to-bcci-for-world-cup-golden-ticket-recipients-4388861%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhopefully-ms-dhoni-isro-chief-also-sunil-gavaskar-gives-wish-list-to-bcci-for-world-cup-golden-ticket-recipients-4388861%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhopefully-ms-dhoni-isro-chief-also-sunil-gavaskar-gives-wish-list-to-bcci-for-world-cup-golden-ticket-recipients-4388861%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Barbie%20officially%20launches%20Oscar%202024%20campaign%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694696642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103667362%2Cimgsize-29894.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.co