s%20in%20Spain's%20women's%20football%20league%20have%20called%20off%20a%20strike%20after%20reaching%20a%20deal%20to%20increase%20their%20minimum%20wage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fspains-female-footballers-call-off-strike-after-deal-reached-in-pay-row-12961214%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fspains-female-footballers-call-off-strike-after-deal-reached-in-pay-row-12961214%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fspains-female-footballers-call-off-strike-after-deal-reached-in-pay-row-12961214%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jana%20Sena-TDP%20Alliance%3A%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20Makes%20it%20Official%20After%20Meeting%20Naidu%20in%20Jail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14165831%2FF5-WFXXa0AA-5uv.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20of%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20the%20skill%20development%20scam%20seems%20to%20have%20helped%20cement%20the%20much-awaited%20TDP-Jana%20Sena%20alliance%20%E2%80%93%20a%20development%20that%20could%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%202024%20elections%20to%20the%20Assembly%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJana%20Sena%20and%20TDP%20will%20contest%20the%20elections%20together%20next%20year.%20I%20have%20faith%20in%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20declared%20Jana%20Sena%20president%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20on%20Thursday%2C%20September%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20after%20a%20meeting%20the%20actor-politician%20had%20with%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20in%20the%20company%20of%20TDP%20leader%20and%20actor%20N.%20Balakrishna%2C%20and%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20TDP%20general%20secretary%20Nara%20Lokesh%2C%20at%20the%20Rajamahendravaram%20Central%20Jail%20during%20%E2%80%9Cmulaqat%E2%80%9D%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPawan%20Kalyan%20announced%20the%20alliance%20after%20discussing%20the%20political%20climate%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20alleged%20vindictive%20politics%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmphasises%20need%20to%20oust%20YSRCP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20chief%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20oust%20the%20YSRCP%20government%20at%20the%20hustings%20and%20expressed%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20would%20join%20the%20effort.%20He%20stated%20that%20his%20primary%20goal%20was%20to%20put%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20back%20on%20the%20road%20to%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20referred%20to%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20as%20a%20seasoned%20politician%20and%20labelled%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20as%20an%20economic%20offender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPawan%20Kalyan%20lamented%20the%20imprisonment%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Carchitect%20of%20Cyberabad%E2%80%9D%20and%20expressed%20his%20intention%20to%20bring%20this%20issue%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%2C%20highlighting%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%20treatment%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Andhra%20government.%20He%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20providing%20proper%20security%20to%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPawan%20Kalyan%C2%A0has%20long%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fandhrapradesh%2Fjana-sena-tdp-alliance-all-but-sealed-as-pawan-kalyan-meets-chandrababu-naidu%2F%5C%22%3Eadvocating%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20alliance%20of%20all%20Opposition%20parties%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%2C%20to%20challenge%20the%20YSRCP%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20reluctant%20to%20confirm%20its%20participation%20in%20this%20three-party%20alliance%2C%20despite%20its%20desire%20to%20have%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20on%20its%20side.%20The%20BJP%20and%20Jana%20Sena%20are%20in%20a%20formal%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20meeting%20with%20Naidu%2C%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20made%20an%20unequivocal%20statement%20about%20the%20alliance%20with%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMakes%20stand%20clear%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tone%20of%20his%20speech%20indicated%20that%20his%20decision%20was%20final%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20BJP%20approved%20of%20it%20or%20not.%20It%20seemed%20like%20a%20message%20to%20the%20BJP%20to%20chart%20its%20course%20if%20it%20was%20unwilling%20to%20cooperate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20has%20previously%20shown%20support%20for%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20he%20had%20never%20been%20this%20explicit%20about%20contesting%20elections%20in%20alliance%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20may%20have%20occurred%20because%20the%20BJP%20reportedly%20had%20reservations%20about%20Naidu%20and%20did%20not%20want%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20to%20associate%20with%20him.%20However%2C%20the%20actor-politician%20has%20now%20made%20his%20support%20clear%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CMy%20decision%20may%20not%20please%20some%20people.%20I%20was%20the%20first%20person%20from%20South%20India%20to%20support%20Narendra%20Modi%20because%20I%20believed%20the%20nation%20needed%20a%20strong%20leader.%20When%20I%20supported%20Modi%2C%20many%20people%20criticised%20my%20decision.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20not%20go%20back%20on%20my%20stand%20once%20I%20take%20a%20decision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Jana%20Sena%20chief%20clarified%20that%20he%20had%20never%20met%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20his%20own%20and%20that%20each%20meeting%20was%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20invitation.%20He%20stated%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20waste%20such%20leaders%E2%80%99%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpresses%20confidence%20in%20Naidu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe