0to%20insult%20the%20modesty%20of%20a%20woman)%2C%20and%20under%20non-bailable%20provisions%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20%26amp%3B%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20chronology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBagchi%2C%20an%20ABP%20reporter%20for%2012%20years%20and%20at%20present%20the%20paper%E2%80%99s%20Kharagpur%20correspondent%2C%20recently%20wrote%20two%20reports%20highlighting%20illegal%20hooch%20trade%20in%20the%20Patnapara%20area%20of%20Sanjoal%20in%20Kharagpur%E2%80%99s%20Ward%20No%2024.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20appeared%20on%20August%2026%20and%20the%20second%20on%20August%2029.%20None%20of%20the%20reports%20carried%20his%20byline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20August%2026%20report%C2%A0(headlined%20%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BF%E0%A7%9F%E0%A7%87%20%E0%A6%9A%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%87%20%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BE%2C%20%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%20%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%B6%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%A8%2F%20Hooch%20trade%20flourishes%2C%20no%20action%20from%20administration)%2C%20stated%20that%20some%20women%20from%20the%20above-mentioned%20locality%20had%20filed%20a%20written%20complaint%20with%20Kharagpur%20Town%20police%20about%20the%20flourishing%20illegal%20liquor%20trade%20in%20a%20residential%20area.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20Basanti%20Das.%20The%20report%20talked%20about%20their%20demands%20and%20the%20responses%20from%20the%20local%20councillor%20and%20the%20municipality%20chairman.%20It%20also%20described%20in%20detail%20how%20the%20hooch%20trade%20was%20going%20on%20from%20shanties%20and%20even%20boys%20and%20girls%20as%20young%20as%2012%20or%2013%20were%20involved%20in%20it.%20The%20area%20was%20thronged%20by%20drunkards%20round%20the%20clock%20and%20this%20had%20vitiated%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20the%20locality%2C%20women%20told%20the%20reporter.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20the%20hooch%20sellers%20would%20boast%20that%20they%20had%20been%20in%20this%20business%20for%2030%20years%20and%20no%20one%20could%20do%20anything%20to%20stop%20them.%20The%20local%20councillor%20expressed%20his%20helplessness%20and%20said%20that%20he%20had%20repeatedly%20informed%20the%20police%20about%20the%20menace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2029%2C%20a%20follow-up%20story%20was%20published%20in%20ABP%20(headlined%20%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%AD%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AF%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%97%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%80%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0%20%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A7%9C%E0%A6%BF%20%E0%A6%98%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%93%20%E0%A6%9A%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%87%20%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0%2C%20%E0%A6%B9%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%93%2F%20Hooch%20traders%20gherao%20and%20threaten%20complainants).%20This%20report%20stated%20that%20on%20the%20night%20of%20Sunday%2C%20August%2027%2C%20police%20raided%20the%20area%20and%20detained%20some%20drunkards.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20police%20stated%20that%20the%20hooch%20sellers%20were%20%E2%80%98alert%E2%80%99%20and%20hence%20no%20one%20of%20them%20could%20be%20arrested%20during%20the%20raid%20on%20Sunday.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20illegal%20hooch%20sellers%20raided%20the%20houses%20of%20complainants%20Basanti%20Das%20and%20Bandana%20Patra%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20kicked%20their%20doors%20and%20threatened%20them%20of%20dire%20consequences%20if%20the%20complaint%20was%20not%20withdrawn.%20The%20women%20alleged%20that%20they%20had%20made%20repeated%20calls%20to%20police%20during%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20they%20turned%20up%20about%20an%20hour%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20accessed%20videos%20of%20one%20such%20spurious%20liquor%20outlet%20from%20the%20area.%20A%20woman%20can%20be%20seen%20bringing%20a%20plastic%20bottle%20with%20a%20colourless%20liquid%20in%20it%20from%20inside%20a%20shanty%20and%20serving%20a%20man%20who%20drinks%20from%20a%20glass.%20A%20plastic%20sheet%20has%20been%20placed%20apparently%20in%20a%20way%20that%20this%20is%20hidden%20from%20the%20public%20eye.%20Another%20man%20can%20be%20seen%20standing%20and%20drinking%2C%20while%20another%20man%20gets%20up%20and%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbengal-press-freedom-journalist-arrest-debmalya-bagchi%5C%22%3EA%20Journalist%E2%80%99s%20Arrest%20in%20Bengal%20Points%20to%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20Worsening%20Media%20Freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20took%20an%20unexpected%20turn%20when%20a%20written%20complaint%20by%20a%20certain%20Saraswati%20Singh%20dated%C2%A0August%2028%20surfaced%2C%20in%20which%20she%20accused%20Bagchi%20and%20anti-hooch%20activist%20Basanti%20Das%20of%20verbally%20abusing%20them%20with%20casteist%20slurs.%20She%20also%20accused%20Bagchi%20of%20pulling%20at%20and%20tearing%20her%20clothes%20and%20physically%20assaulting%20her.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20at%207.30pm%20on%20August%2027%2C%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20hooch%20sellers%20had%20raided%20the%20houses%20of%20Das%20and%20Patra.%20At%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20complaint%20she%20identified%20herself%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20scheduled%20tribe.%20An%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20based%20on%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20arrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20before%204%20am%20on%20September%206%2C%20police%20from%20Kharagpur%20Town%20PS%20led%20by%20sub-inspector%20Purushottam%20Pandey%20reached%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20where%20he%20lived%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20one-year-old%20daughter%20and%20aged%20parents%2C%20and%20shouted%20at%20him%20to%20come%20out.%20Around%205%2C%20he%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20Facebook%20expressing%20his%20dismay%20at%20the%20turn%20of%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20data-show-text%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdebmalyabagchi%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0AVJyX5qcU35KbgVkEFsEjUZ9NxrVqTRiTdXFsxSRQvNDndmDg7DQ2idB8ZPVoU6pl%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20readers%20should%20note%20that%20being%20a%20journalist%2C%20Bagchi%20was%20in%20regular%20contact%20with%20local%20and%20district-level%20police%20officials.%20The%20manner%20in%20which%20his%20house%20was%20raided%20in%20the%20dead%20of%20night%2C%20has%2C%20therefore%2C%20raised%20many%20eyebrows.%20One%20of%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20family%20members%2C%20still%20in%20shock%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20Alt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20could%20have%20just%20called%20him%20up%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20meet%20them%20at%20the%20station.%20Such%20midnight%20raids%20are%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20dens%20of%20history-sheeters%20or%20wanted%20criminals.%20We%20are%20yet%20to%20understand%20why%20such%20action%20was%20necessary%20against%20an%20honest%2C%20well-meaning%20journalist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBagchi%E2%80%99s%20family%20members%20said%20he%20then%20called%20up%20his%20superiors%20at%20ABP%20and%20reporters%20and%20colleagues%20in%20Kharagpur%20and%20Midnapore%20town.%20Most%20of%20them%20suggested%20him%20to%20stay%20put.%20He%20also%20made%20repeated%20calls%20to%20the%20Kharagpur%20Town%20IC%20and%20West%20Midnapore%20SP%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20response%20from%20them.%20The%20policemen%20waited%20in%20front%20of%20his%20house%20till%208%20am.%20The%20ABP%20office%20in%20Kolkata%20advised%20Bagchi%20to%20go%20to%20the%20PS%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20meet%20the%20IC.%20This%20was%20corroborated%20to%20%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20a%20senior%20ABP%20journalist%20based%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2010.15%20am%2C%20Bagchi%20left%20his%20home%20on%20another%20reporter%E2%80%99s%20bike%20for%20the%20police%20station.%20He%20was%20arrested%20at%2011.30%20am.%20Basanti%20Das%2C%20too%2C%20was%20arrested%20from%20her%20home%20earlier%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20Both%20of%20them%20were%20produced%20in%20West%20Midnapore%20district%20court%20and%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20till%20September%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20readers%20should%20note%20in%20August%202022%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2022%2F08%2F29%2Fcomplete-lawlessness-supreme-court-slams-jharkhand-government-over-journalists-arrest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20had%20pulled%20up%20the%20Jharkhand%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20arresting%20a%20journalist%20from%20his%20home%20at%20midnight.%20Refusing%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20Jharkhand%20High%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20granting%20interim%20bail%20to%20journalist%20Arup%20Chatterjee%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20Hima%20Kohli%20took%20note%20of%20the%20disregard%20for%20the%20code%20of%20conduct.%20%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20how%20the%20state%20of%20Jharkhand%20is%20harassing%20a%20journalist.%20This%20is%20an%20excess%20of%20state%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandrachud%20said.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20go%20to%20his%20house%20at%2012%20o%E2%80%99clock%20at%20night%2C%20pull%20him%20out%20of%20his%20bedroom%E2%80%A6This%20is%20no%20way%20to%20treat%20a%20journalist.%20This%20is%20complete%20lawlessness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20Midnapore%20SP%20Dhritiman%20Sarkar%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20repeated%20calls%20and%20text%20messages%20from%20%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Town%20IC%20Rajib%20Pal%20said%20he%20was%20on%20leave.%20Investigating%20officer%20and%20deputy%20SP%20Shaymal%20Mondal%E2%80%99s%20phone%20was%20found%20switched%20off.%20This%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20there%20is%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20discrepancies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20news%20portal%20named%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_-aqJorhNXk%3Fsi%3DKpX1NaPbC07Cd59e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESambad%20Titumeer%3C%2Fem%3E%20uploaded%20a%20bulletin%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20its%20YouTube%20channel%20on%20September%208%20under%20the%20headline%20%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%9C%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8B%20%E0%A6%95%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B8%20%E0%A6%A6%E0%A6%BF%E0%A7%9F%E0%A7%87%20%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%20%E0%A6%9C%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%87%20%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B2%20%E0%A6%86%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A6%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%9C%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%20%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%A4%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%20%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%82%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%95%E0%A7%87%2C%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%81-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%9F%20%E0%A6%AB%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%81%E0%A6%B8%20%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%B2%20%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A4%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A4%E0%A6%A6%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A4%E0%A7%87%20(Police%20sends%20ABP%20journalist%20to%20jail%20in%20fake%20case.%20Investigation%20reveals%20blue-print).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bulletin%20plays%20out%20a%20telephonic%20conversation%20between%20a%20male%20voice%20and%20a%20female%20voice.%20The%20presenter%20identifies%20them%20as%20a%20correspondent%20of%20the%20outlet%20named%20Briti%20Sundar%20Roy%20and%20the%20complainant%2C%20Saraswati%20Singh.%C2%A0In%20the%20conversation%2C%20the%20woman%20admits%20that%20she%20does%20not%20know%20Deblamya%20Bagchi.%20She%20says%20she%20filed%20the%20complaint%20against%20him%20because%20she%20found%20out%20that%20his%20reports%20caused%20all%20the%20police%20action.%20She%20also%20admits%20that%20no%20incident%20of%20%E2%80%98assault%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98outraging%20her%20modesty%E2%80%99%20had%20taken%20place%20and%20she%20had%20named%20Bagchi%20in%20the%20complaint%20because%20she%20was%20%E2%80%98angry%20with%20him%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20says%20that%20she%20is%20an%20unlettered%20woman%2C%20and%20the%20complaint%20was%20written%20by%20a%20relative.%20Through%20out%20the%20conversation%2C%20she%20also%20insisted%20on%20having%20no%20involvement%20in%20hooch%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20the%20recorded%20conversation%20from%20the%20journalist%2C%20Briti%20Sundar%20Roy%2C%20who%20spoke%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoy%20confirmed%20to%20us%20that%20it%20was%20indeed%20him%20speaking%20to%20Singh%20and%20she%20admitted%20that%20no%20such%20incident%20as%20alleged%20in%20the%20complaint%20had%20taken%20place.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20audio%20clip%20is%20completely%20authentic.%20I%20spoke%20to%20her.%20As%20you%20can%20hear%2C%20she%20admitted%20without%20any%20coercion%20from%20me%20that%20the%20allegations%20were%20made%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roy%20told%20%3Cem%3EAlt%20News.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20asked%20Roy%20to%20send%20a%20screenshot%20of%20his%20call%20log.%20We%20verified%20that%20he%20had%20called%20the%20complainant%20and%20had%20a%20conversation%20for%2018%20minutes%2036%20seconds%2C%20and%20the%20same%20conversation%20was%20played%20out%20in%20the%20YouTube%20bulletin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3Ecalled%20up%20Saraswati%20Singh%2C%20she%20told%20us%20she%20would%20only%20speak%20in%20court.%20When%20asked%20if%20she%20told%20a%20journalist%20over%20phone%20that%20she%20had%20made%20up%20the%20allegations%2C%20she%20disconnected%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20which%20Bagchi%20and%20Das%20were%20arrested%2C%20they%20had%20assaulted%20Saraswati%20Singh%20at%207.30%20pm%20on%20the%20night%20of%20Sunday%2C%20August%2027.%20According%20to%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20second%20report%2C%20it%20was%20the%20same%20time%20when%20a%20group%20of%20hooch%20sellers%20raided%20the%20houses%20of%20Das%20and%20others%2C%20who%20had%20protested%20against%20hooch%20trade.%20%E2%80%9CSaraswati%20Singh%20is%20a%20hooch%20seller.%20Basanti%20Das%20told%20us%20SIngh%20was%20among%20the%20women%20who%20raided%20their%20homes.%20The%20complaints%20against%20Bagchi%20are%20made%20up%20by%20Singh.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20she%20was%20acting%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20anyone.%20But%20the%20matter%20is%20totally%20false.%20She%20was%20upset%20at%20the%20trouble%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20reports%20caused%20to%20her%20business.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20she%20acted%20out%20of%20vengeance%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20journalist%20told%3Cem%3E%20Alt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJournalists%20condemn%20police%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBagchi%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Sourav%20Ghosh%20told%3Cem%3E%20Alt%20News%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20allegation%20against%20Bagchi%20is%20false.%20Police%20did%20not%20seek%20custody%20because%20they%20know%20there%20is%20no%20merit%20in%20the%20complaint.%20A%20journalist%20is%20duty%20bound%20to%20expose%20any%20illegality.%20Debmalya%20did%20his%20job.%20The%20environment%20of%20the%20whole%20locality%20was%20being%20spoilt%20by%20hooch%20trade.%20It%20had%20become%20a%20den%20of%20anti-socials.%20Illegal%20liquor%20trade%20is%20a%20social%20ill.%20Hence%2C%20Debmalya%20wrote%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20police%20action%20against%20his%20client%2C%20Ghosh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20a%20journalist%20like%20Bagchi%20could%20have%20been%20treated%20better.%20They%20could%20have%20informed%20him%20of%20the%20FIR%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20report%20to%20the%20PS.%20In%20stead%2C%20they%20raided%20his%20house%20past%20midnight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDhrubojyoti%20Pramanik%2C%20a%20senior%20editor%20at%20%3Cem%3ENews18%3C%2Fem%3E%20condemned%20the%20police%20action%20against%20Bagchi%20on%20Facebook.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.%20Debmalya%20has%20repeatedly%20written%20on%20several%20issues%20including%20sand%20mafia%2C%20hooch%20cycle%2C%20Kharagpur%20railway%20mafia%20in%20West%20Midnapore%20district%20fearlessly%20and%20in%20public%20interest.%20I%20believe%20court%20will%20look%20into%20whether%20his%20reporting%20on%20these%20issues%20have%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20his%20arrest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata%20Press%20Club%20president%20met%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20at%20her%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20office%20on%20September%207%20and%20apprised%20her%20of%20the%20matter.%20According%20to%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20press%20club%2C%20she%20spoke%20to%20the%20local%20police%20administration%20and%20gave%20necessary%20instructions.%20She%20also%20promised%20that%20the%20case%20would%20be%20handled%20with%20sensitivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ABP%20top%20brass%20(chief%20editor%20and%20publisher%20Atideb%20Sarkar%2C%20editor%20Ishani%20Dutta%20Ray%20and%20senior%20editors%20Debanjana%20Bhattacharya%20and%20Debasish%20Choudhury)%20met%20Bagchi%20at%20Midnapore%20central%20jail%20on%20September%2011.%20Several%20rallies%20and%20protest%20marches%20were%20taken%20out%20across%20the%20state%20on%20September%2013%20condemning%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202011%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fkolkata-news%2F2011-bengal-hooch-tragedy-main-accused-gets-life-sentence-till-death-101627906226744.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E172%20people%20had%20lost%20their%20lives%20consuming%20spurious%20liquor%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20South%2024%20Parganas%20district.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20main%20accused%2C%20Noor%20Ahmed%20Fakir%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20imprisonment%20until%20natural%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Fabp-reporters-arrest-in-bengal-veracity-of-complaint-police-excesses-under-scanner%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2F%5C%22%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fa