%20that%20there%20are%20some%20challenges%20going%20forward%20that%20need%20to%20be%20resolved%20before%20finalising%20who%20gets%20to%20contest%20what.%20The%20source%20further%20added%20that%20Yediyurappa%E2%80%99s%20comments%20also%20indicate%20that%20such%20sensitive%20matter%20is%20left%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20high%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694676020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F01101931%2Fyediyurappa.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-shah-will-decide-on-seat-sharing-with-jds-yediyurappa-strikes-a-cautious-note%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20Yediyurappa%20who%20first%20confirmed%20the%20BJP-JD(S)%20electoral%20alliance%20on%20September%208%2C%20going%20as%20far%20as%20announcing%20that%20the%20latter%20would%20get%20four%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20to%20contest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-shah-will-decide-on-seat-sharing-with-jds-yediyurappa-strikes-a-cautious-note%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Shockingly%20insensitive'%3A%20Officer%20joked%20after%20woman%20hit%20and%20killed%20by%20police%20car%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694671380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-seattle-police-jaahnavi-kandula_6284051.jpg%3F20230914074214%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fseattle-police-officer-recorded-laughing-after-woman-killed-in-fatal-crash-12960858%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Seattle%20police%20officer%20is%20under%20investigation%20after%20being%20recorded%20joking%20about%20a%20woman%20hit%20and%20killed%20by%20a%20police%20car.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fseattle-police-officer-recorded-laughing-after-woman-killed-in-fatal-crash-12960858%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fseattle-police-officer-recorded-laughing-after-woman-killed-in-fatal-crash-12960858%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fseattle-police-officer-recorded-laughing-after-woman-killed-in-fatal-crash-12960858%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Madurai%20Doctor%20is%20Taking%20Healthcare%20Directly%20to%20the%20Doorsteps%20of%2025000%20Senior%20Citizens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20food%20can%20be%20delivered%20to%20your%20doorstep%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20quality%20healthcare%20too%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20C.%20Taking%20this%20thought%20forward%2C%20in%202019%2C%20he%20started%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328138%2Fmadurai-dr-swaminathan-doctor-on-wheels-takes-affordable-healthcare-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98Doctor%20on%20Wheels%E2%80%99%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ean%20initiative%20to%20give%20patients%20medical%20services%20at%20their%20doorsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Canada%2C%20Swaminathan%20moved%20to%20India%20for%20higher%20studies%20in%20medicine.%20In%202015%2C%20after%20completing%20his%20MBBS%20and%20post-graduation%20in%20emergency%20medicine%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20a%20private%20medical%20college%20in%20the%20intensive%20care%20unit%20as%20a%20junior%20consultant%20for%20five%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20felt%20that%20a%20corporate%20job%20is%20not%20my%20cup%20of%20tea.%20I%20wanted%20to%20offer%20something%20better%20to%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20meet%20a%20lot%20of%20senior%20citizens%20at%20the%20hospital.%20Often%2C%20they%E2%80%99d%20narrate%20the%20logistical%20difficulties%20they%20face%20while%20shifting%20from%20their%20homes%20