ing-doctor-free-delivery-girl-child-equality%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20saving%20money%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20kids%20can%20deposit%20their%20weekly%20points%20in%20the%20bank%20and%20save%20them.%20They%20can%20keep%20collecting%20them%20and%20buy%20something%20expensive%20too.%20For%20example%2C%20many%20kids%20saved%20up%20for%20months%20and%20were%20able%20to%20buy%20mobile%20phones%20with%20the%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Learning%20by%20Doing%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20is%20affiliated%20to%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Akshar%20School%2C%20we%20place%20students%20in%20the%20grade%20levels%20that%20they%20are%20at%20based%20on%20an%20aptitude%20test.%20So%2C%20if%20a%20student%20excels%20in%206th%20standard%20maths%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%E2%80%99ll%20study.%20But%20if%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20comfortable%20with%203rd-standard%20science%2C%20then%20their%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmita%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20provides%20an%20opportunity%20for%20older%20students%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20attend%20school%20earlier%2C%20perhaps%20due%20to%20poverty%2C%20to%20catch%20up%20and%20learn%20at%20their%20own%20pace%2C%20she%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20helped%20us%20connect%20with%20those%20older%20kids%20very%20well%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Yuvraj%20Kashyap%20(now%2020)%20joined%20Akshar%20School%20as%20a%20student%20back%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20taken%20aback%20by%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20unique%20curriculum%20and%20fee%20policy.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20true%20paradigm%20shift%20in%20every%20sense%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yuvraj%20reminisces%20in%20a%20chat%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20his%20eyes%20gleaming%20with%20excitement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-caption