ur-barren-land-to-heritage-property%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20QR%20Code%20Shows%20if%20Drinking%20Water%20Cans%20Are%20Safe%20to%20Use%2C%20Thanks%20to%202%20Brothers%20From%20Chennai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Supriya%20Sethuram%20has%20been%20dependent%20on%20water%20cans%20for%20her%20daily%20drinking%20water%20needs.%20However%2C%20the%20local%20suppliers%20of%20these%20cans%20would%20often%20deliver%20dirty%20or%20cloudy%20cans%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mother%20of%20two%20children%20aged%2011%20and%209%2C%20she%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20she%20offered%20her%20children%20to%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20forced%20to%20fulfill%20our%20daily%20drinking%20needs%20from%20these%20cans%20as%20the%20tap%20water%20here%20is%20not%20clean.%20But%20whether%20I%20will%20be%20supplied%20with%20a%20clean%20can%20or%20a%20bad%20one%20would%20depend%20on%20the%20stock%20that%20the%20shopkeeper%20receives%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2040-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFed%20up%20with%20this%20situation%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20went%20to%20the%20spot%20where%20these%20water%20cans%20were%20unloaded.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20all%20the%20cans%20were%20irresponsibly%20thrown%20around.%20Chennai%20is%20a%20very%20hot%20place.%20When%20plastic%20cans%20are%20left%20outside%20in%20the%20heat%2C%20they%20go%20bad%20making%20the%20water%2C%20or%20any%20content%2C%20unfit%20for%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%20six%20months%20back%2C%20upon%20her%20friend%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%2C%20she%20switched%20to%20using%20water%20cans%20by%20%E2%80%98BookWater%E2%80%99.%20The%20company%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20IoT%20(Internet%20of%20Things)-powered%20and%20quality-based%20water%20delivery%20platform%20in%20the%20world%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20scan%20the%20QR%20code%20on%20its%20water%20cans%20and%20get%20details%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20cans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1694173006.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founders%20of%20BookWater%20--%20Balachander%2C%20Bharath%2C%20Sameer%20and%20Hariharan.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1694173006.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1694173006-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1694173006-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1694173006-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1694173006-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329454%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20left%20to%20right%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20Balachander%2C%20Bharath%2C%20Sameer%20and%20Hariharan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20interested%20me%20because%20by%20simply%20scanning%20the%20QR%20code%2C%20you%20can%20know%20details%20on%20how%20many%20times%20the%20can%20has%20been%20used%20so%20far.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20any%20other%20company%20does%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20this%20innovation%20are%20brothers%20Bharath%20Govindaraghavan%20and%20Balachander%20G.%C2%A0%20Along%20with%20their%20friends%2C%20Hariharan%20Vedamurthy%20and%20Sameer%20Bharat%20Ram%2C%20they%20co-founded%20BookWater.%20The%20startup%20delivers%20about%2050%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F279908%2Fcaro-water-india-first-eco-friendly-drinking-water-box-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20cans%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20QR%20codes%20every%20month%20across%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20you%20swig%20from%20a%20plastic%20can%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalachander%20is%20a%20graduate%20in%20environmental%20law%20from%20the%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20whereas%20Bharath%20is%20an%20electronics%20engineer%20by%20profession.%20After%20working%20with%20several%20companies%2C%20the%20Chennai-based%20brothers%20got%20together%20to%20work%20in%20the%20water%20space%20that%20is%20governed%20by%20unorganised%20players%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Balachander%20(46)%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Chennai%2C%20people%20are%20dependent%20on%20water%20tanks%20for%20their%20daily%20water%20needs%20as%20the%20groundwater%20is%20very%20polluted%20or%20it%20is%20so%20saline%20that%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20use.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%2C%20more%20than%2025%20lakh%20cans%20of%2020-litre%20capacity%20are%20sold%20in%20Chennai.%20Even%20the%20poorest%20here%20are%20dependent%20on%20water%20cans%20that%20cost%20Rs%2035-45.%20But%20no%20one%20really%20knows%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20and%20of%20these%20cans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20plastic%20water%20cans%20are%20also%20overused.%20You%20are%20not%20supposed%20to%20reuse%20these%20water%20cans%20beyond%20a%20certain%20extent%20after%20which%2C%20they%20start%20to%20lose%20their%20transparency.%20But%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20cans%20you%20see%20in%20the%20market%20will%20be%20completely%20clouded%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20happens%20due%20to%20the%20cans%20being%20left%20un